2%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68486536.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20Minister%20Regrets%20Statement%20On%20Indian%20Migrant%20Workers%2C%20Apologises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELabour%20Minister%20Hsu%20Ming-chun%20issued%20an%20apology%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20her%20remarks%20regarding%20the%20planned%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20migrant%20workers%2C%20which%20some%20have%20criticised%20as%20%26quot%3Bracist%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20reported%20by%20Central%20News%20Agency%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%2C%20Minister%20Hsu%20had%20stated%20that%20the%20ministry%20would%20initially%20focus%20on%20recruiting%20workers%20from%20northeastern%20India%20because%20'their%20skin%20colour%20and%20dietary%20habits%20are%20closer%20to%20ours.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20stated%20that%20'individuals%20in%20this%20region%2C%20mostly%20Christians%2C%20are%20skilled%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20farming%2C%20as%20per%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20(MOFA)%20assessments%2C'%20as%20per%20Central%20News%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20legislative%20hearing%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20Hsu%20expressed%20regret%20for%20her%20'inaccurate'%20comments%2C%20clarifying%20that%20Taiwan's%20labour%20policies%20aim%20for%20equality%2C%20devoid%20of%20discrimination%2C%20be%20it%20for%20local%20or%20foreign%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Central%20News%20Agency%2C%20she%20emphasized%20her%20intention%20to%20highlight%20the%20abilities%20and%20performance%20of%20Indian%20workers%2C%20dissociating%20from%20any%20discriminatory%20motives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegislator%20Chen%20Kuan-ting%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20strongly%20condemned%20Hsu's%20remarks%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3Bstrongly%20condemned%26quot%3B%20Hsu's%20comments%2C%20arguing%20that%20skin%20colour%20and%20race%20should%20not%20be%20criteria%20for%20recruiting%20migrant%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20on%20Monday%20night%2C%20the%20Labor%20Ministry%20apologised%20for%20Hsu's%20'inaccurate'%20choice%20of%20words%2C%20emphasising%20that%20the%20comments%20were%20not%20meant%20to%20discriminate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20also%20issued%20an%20apology%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20'not%20entirely%20appropriate'%20narratives%20surrounding%20the%20planned%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20that%20Taiwan%20boasts%20a%20civil%20society%20that%20embraces%20different%20views%20and%20allows%20for%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20voices%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaiwan%20also%20fully%20respects%20India's%20diverse%20and%20rich%20culture%20and%20cherishes%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20peoples%20of%20Taiwan%20and%20India.%20It%20will%20spare%20no%20effort%20in%20advancing%20cultural%20exchanges%20and%20mutual%20understanding%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20further%20elevating%20cooperation%20and%20partnership%20between%20Taiwan%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20further%20expressed%20hope%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Taiwan%20will%20support%20the%20country's%20efforts%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20world%20and%20advance%20substantive%20interactions%20with%20partners%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaiwan%20government%20also%20hopes%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Taiwan%20will%20support%20the%20country's%20efforts%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20world%2C%20further%20advance%20substantive%20interactions%20with%20partners%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20and%20thereby%20bolster%20reciprocal%20and%20mutually%20beneficial%20exchanges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20be