0of%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20finalised%20soon%2C%20once%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20approves%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20that%20such%20a%20scheme%20to%20give%20'right%20to%20employment'%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20and%20some%20allowance%20may%20also%20be%20offered%20to%20the%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20developed%20countries%20do%20not%20offer%20their%20youth%20such%20a%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20would%20also%20provide%20for%20a%20stringent%20law%20and%20punishment%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20country%20and%20will%20suggest%20measures%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20government%20recruitments%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20come%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20has%20focussed%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students%20suffering%20due%20to%20frequent%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cancellation%20of%20exams%20thereafter%20in%20some%20cases%20like%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thrust%20of%20the%20manifesto%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20on%20the%205-nyay%20(five%20pillars%20of%20justice)%20promised%20by%20the%20Congress%20during%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20would%20also%20focus%20on%20giving%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20minimum%20support%20price%20and%20promising%20a%20caste-based%20census%20in%20the%20country%20for%20filling%20up%20the%20government%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20likely%20to%20give%20a%20thrust%20to%20some%20welfare%20measures%20like%20providing%20financial%20assistance%20to%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20ensuring%20that%20they%20get%20justice%20and%20be%20part%20of%20the%20state%20welfare%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20Congress%20promises%20made%20to%20the%20people%20helped%20the%20party%20get%20into%20power%20in%20states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20recently.%20The%20Congress%20manifesto%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20union%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20met%20here%20to%20give%20a%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20at%20a%20five-hour%20meeting%20last%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20members%20of%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20committee%20were%20present%20during%20the%20meeting%20at%20the%20AICC%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChidambaram%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20given%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20draft%20manifesto%20which%20will%20become%20the%20party%20document%20once%20the%20CWC%20approves%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20wound%20up%20internal%20deliberations%20for%20giving%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20party%20manifesto%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20include%20some%20innovative%20measures%20like%20an%20apprenticeship%20scheme%20for%20the%20youth%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20completed%20our%20draft%20manifesto.%20It's%20a%20draft.%20It%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20working%20committee.%20It%20is%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20which%20finalises%20the%20manifesto%20and%20then%20it%20becomes%20a%20Congress%20party%20document.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20have%20completed%20the%20work%20on%20the%20draft%20manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20Chidambaram%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20to%20be%20able%20to%20present%20it%20to%20the%20Congress%20president%20along%20with%20members%20available%20in%20Delhi%20sometime%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20manifesto%20committee%20also%20has%20senior%20leaders%20like%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20and%20Anand%20Sharma%2C%20among%20others.%20Vadra%20and%20Sharma%20were%2C%20however%2C%20not%20present%20in%20the%20meetings%20held%20on%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20discussions%20on%20Tuesday%20include%20Chidambaram%20and%20Tharoor%2C%20minority%20chief%20head%20Imran%20Pratapgarhi%2C%20Ranjeet%20Ranjan%20and%20Gurdeep%20Sappal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratapgarhi%20after%20the%20meeting%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20taken%20views%20from%20all%20across%20the%20country%20and%20compiled%20it%20accordingly.%20It%20combines%20everything%2C%20youth%20women%2C%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%20etc.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20go%20now%20to%20the%20CWC%20and%20will%20notify%20upon%20issued%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ranjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20the%20party%20manifesto%20will%20focus%20on%20empowering%20the%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20poor%20and%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20the%20party%20is%20mulling%20a%20plan%20to%20tackle%20the%20menace%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20present%20its%20vision%20for%20bringing%20about%20transparency%20in%20government%20recruitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2016-member%20panel%20includes%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20former%20union%20minister%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20while%20former%20Chhattisgarh%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%20is%20its%20convenor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709686740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F5tnc6udo_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_08_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-to-promise-right-to-employment-to-youth-in-2024-lok-sabha-poll-manifesto-5184535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seeking%20to%20woo%20the%20country's%20youth%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20offer%20them%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20employment%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20its%20poll%20promise%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-to-promise-right-to-employment-to-youth-in-2024-lok-sabha-poll-manifesto-5184535%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Courts%20To%20Votes%3A%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20And%20His%20Many%20Controversies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20had%20run-ins%20with%20lawyers%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20a%20fellow%20judge%20during%20his%20tenure%20at%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20and%20had%20even%20been%20pulled%20up%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20giving%20an%20interview%20on%20a%20scam%20while%20hearing%20cases%20related%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20taken%20several%20unprecedented%20steps%20in%20his%20career%2C%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20has%20taken%20another%20-%C2%A0%20becoming%20the%20first%20high%20court%20judge%20in%20recent%20memory%20to%20resign%20and%20join%20a%20political%20party.%20The%20former%20judge%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20gave%20an%20interview%20to%20a%20Bengali%20news%20channel%20on%20the%20alleged%20job-for-bribe%20scam%2C%20in%20which%20he%20had%20allegedly%20spoken%20against%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20him%20in%20April%202023%20and%20said%20that%20judges%20have%20no%20business%20granting%20interviews%20on%20pending%20matters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20want%20to%20say%20that%20judges%20have%20no%20business%20granting%20interviews%20on%20matters%20which%20are%20pending.%20If%20he%20said%20that%20about%20the%20petitioner%20(Mr%20Banerjee)%2C%20he%20has%20no%20business%20participating%20in%20the%20proceedings.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20a%20judge%20who%20has%20made%20statements%20like%20these%20about%20a%20political%20personality%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20hearings.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20some%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud%20had%20said%20on%20April%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrder%20To%20Supreme%20Court%20Secretary%20General%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20on%20April%2028%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20to%20reassign%20the%20case%20to%20another%20judge%20and%20said%20this%20was%20necessary%20given%20%26quot%3Bthe%20need%20to%20preserve%20public%20confidence%20in%20the%20administration%20of%20justice%26quot%3B.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20issued%20an%20order%20to%20the%20Secretary%20General%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20directing%20that%20the%20documents%20concerning%20his%20removal%20be%20produced%20before%20him%20by%20midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20direct%20the%20Secretary%20General%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20to%20produce%20before%20me%20the%20report%20and%20the%20official%20translation%20of%20the%20interview%20given%20by%20me%20in%20media%20and%20the%20affidavit%20of%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20this%20Court%20in%20original%2C%20forthwith%20by%2012%20midnight%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20order%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20would%20wait%20in%20his%20chamber%20till%2012%3A15%20am%20for%20the%20documents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gangopadhyay's%20order%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20the%20same%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawyer%20Boycott%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20had%20announced%20the%20boycott%20of%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20after%20the%20judge%20had%20ordered%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20lawyer%20from%20his%20courtroom%20on%20charges%20of%20contempt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20order%2C%20issued%20on%20December%2018%2C%20was%20later%20withdrawn%2C%20the%20association%20approached%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20high%20court%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20withdraw%20all%20judicial%20work%20from%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay.%20They%20said%20no%20member%20of%20the%20association%20would%20step%20into%20his%20court%20till%20he%20apologised%20to%20the%20advocate%20in%20question%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gangopadhyay%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20court%20for%20two%20days%20and%20then%20spoke%20to%20the%20members%20of%20the%20bar%20association%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bforget%20any%20misgivings%26quot%3B%2C%20after%20which%20the%20boycott%20was%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJudge%20vs%20Judge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20after%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20justices%20Soumen%20Sen%20and%20Uday%20Kumar%20stayed%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay's%20judgment%20ordering%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20medical%20admissions%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20judge%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Sen%20of%20working%20for%20a%20political%20party.%20He%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20Justices%20Sen%20and%20Kumar%20was%20%26quot%3Bwholly%20illegal%20and%20has%20to%20be%20ignored%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20later%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20stayed%20all%20proceedings%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20including%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay's%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Innings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20confirmed%20his%20resignation%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%