ial%20melting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20drivers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearth-axis-shifted-melting-ice-climate-change-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglacial%20melting%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20flow%20of%20warm%2C%20salty%20sea%20water%20deep%20within%20the%20ocean.%20These%20warm%20currents%20lap%20against%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20Thwaites%2C%20for%20example%2C%20melting%20away%20the%20thick%20ice%20that%20keeps%20the%20shelf's%20edge%20from%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20oceans%20warm%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstill-time-to-address-climate-change-ipcc-scientists-report-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20intruding%20currents%20will%20increasingly%20erode%20the%20Thwaites%2C%20driving%20it%20closer%20to%20total%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoore%20and%20his%20colleagues%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20they%20could%20anchor%20curtains%20on%20the%20Amundsen%20seafloor%20to%20slow%20the%20melting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20these%20curtains%20would%20block%20the%20flow%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlantic-ocean-currents-collapse-shut-down-new-study-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarm%20currents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Thwaites%20to%20halt%20melting%20and%20give%20its%20ice%20shelf%20time%20to%20re-thicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221004%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22diagram%20of%20sea%20curtains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e78a036080194819fccd18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20diagram%20shows%20how%20a%20seabed%20anchored%20curtain%20could%20block%20the%20deep%20warm%20water%20currents%20from%20reaching%20glaciers.%3Cp%3EArctic%20Centre%20%2F%20University%20of%20Lapland%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%