he%20said%20in%20his%202004%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BThink%20Like%20a%20Billionaire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20eight%20months%26quot%3B%20choosing%20the%20ballroom%20chairs%20for%20Mar-a-Lago%2C%20he%20said%20in%20the%20same%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223995%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20addresses%20the%20media%20outside%20of%20a%20hearing%20on%20his%20felony%20hush%20money%20trial%20at%20Manhattan%20Criminal%20Court%20on%20Feb.%2015%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce47826fcb546d2d502838%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222779%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20braggadocious%20history%20may%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20him.%3Cp%3EANGELA%20WEISS%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20bragged%20about%20pinching%20literal%20pennies%3A%2050%20of%20them%2C%20to%20be%20exact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Spy%20magazine%20started%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20a%20'Who%20Is%20the%20Cheapest%20Millionaire%26quot%3B%20test%2C%20Trump%20said%20some%2030%20pages%20later%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20sent%20checks%20in%20amounts%20from%20fifty%20cents%20to%20five%20dollars%20to%20a%20list%20of%20millionaires%20throughout%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20a%20check%20for%20fifty%20cents%2C%20and%20we%20at%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20deposited%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20may%20call%20that%20cheap.%20I%20call%20it%20watching%20the%20bottom%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%26quot%3BTrump%3A%20How%20to%20Get%20Rich%2C%26quot%3B%20another%202004%20book%2C%20he%20advised%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20know%20every%20aspect%20of%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20down%20to%20the%20paper%20clips%2C%20you're%20setting%20yourself%20up%20for%20some%20unwelcome%20surprises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20some%20100%20pages%20later%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20good%20thing%20I'm%20an%20active%20type%2C%20or%20this%20might%20tire%20me%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20statements%20prosecutors%20say%20they%20may%20use%20as%20trial%20evidence%2C%20Trump%20shows%20his%20vindictive%20side%2C%20including%20his%20warnings%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20can't%20stomach%20the%20disloyalty%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20getting%20even%20when%20I%20get%20screwed%20by%20someone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20past%20warnings%20of%20swift%20retribution%20against%20all%20who%20wrong%20him%20could%20come%20into%20play%20at%20trial%20if%20he%20argues%20that%20Daniels%20was%20quietly%20paid%20a%20six-figure%20sum%20to%20silence%20her%20claims%20of%20having%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20him%20in%202006%2C%20even%20though%20her%20claims%20were%20false.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Daniels%20was%20shaking%20him%20down%20unjustly%2C%20why%20go%20along%20with%20it%3F%20Why%20part%20with%20%24130%2C000%3F%20Why%20not%20go%20on%20the%20attack%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20bad%20people%20out%20there%20who%20want%20to%20take%20you%20for%20every%20penny%20you%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20complained%20in%20a%20statement%20prosecutors%20want%20to%20use%2C%20also%20from%20his%20book%20%26quot%3BThink%20Big.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20stupid%20and%20gullible%20it%20is%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20someone%20takes%20your%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSo%20watch%20your%20step%20and%20pay%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20side%20has%20argued%20that%20the%2082%20statements%2C%20some%20of%20them%20decades%20old%2C%20should%20be%20excluded%20from%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFailing%20that%2C%20they%20have%20asked%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan%2C%20who%20will%20be%20the%20trial%20judge%2C%20to%20make%20prosecutors%20explain%2C%20stateme