C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20bungalows%20in%20The%20Maldives.%3Cp%3ELevente%20Bodo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20a%20reason%20overwater%20bungalows%20aren't%20as%20popular%20in%20the%20Caribbean%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOverwater%20bungalow%20resorts%20are%20more%20than%2055%20years%20old.%20And%20it%20all%20started%20when%20three%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20Jay%20Carlisle%2C%20Hugh%20Kelley%2C%20and%20Donald%20McCallum%20%E2%80%94%20moved%20to%20French%20Polynesia%20to%20start%20a%20vanilla%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20vanilla%20couldn't%20grow%20on%20the%20land%20they%20bought%2C%20the%20men%20pivoted%20to%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%20They%20bought%20a%20run-down%20hotel%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Moorea%20and%20named%20it%20Bali%20Hai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20%E2%80%94%20who%20became%20known%20as%20the%20Bali%20Hai%20Boys%20%E2%80%94%20built%20other%20hotels%2C%20including%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Ra'i%C4%81tea%2C%20where%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20overwater%20bungalows%20originated.%20As%20this%20resort%20grew%20in%20popularity%2C%20there%20was%20nowhere%20to%20expand%2C%20Hugh%20Kelley's%20daughter%2C%20Vaihiria%20Kelley%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20A%20road%20cut%20off%20one%20side%20of%20the%20resort%2C%20and%20other%20resorts%20neighbored%20Bali%20Hai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20to%20expand%20was%20to%20expand%20out%20over%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20inspiration%20from%20traditional%20Tahitian%20fishing%20huts%2C%20which%20similarly%20sit%20over%20the%20ocean%2C%20the%20men%20built%20the%20first%20overwater%20bungalows%20in%201967.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Ra'i%C4%81tea's%20calm%20waters%20made%20it%20the%20ideal%20place%20for%20an%20overwater%20bungalow%2C%20Kelley%20said.%20The%20trio%20built%20ladders%20leading%20straight%20into%20the%20ocean%20and%20added%20clear%20pa