al%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20from%20building%20these%20structures.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20Sandals%20Resort%20in%20Montego%20Bay%2C%20Jamaica%2C%20was%20the%20first%20resort%20to%20offer%20overwater%20bungalows%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20according%20to%20Cond%C3%A9%20Nast%20Traveler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20resorts%20followed.%20The%20accommodations%20now%20exist%20in%20Aruba%2C%20Panama%2C%20Antigua%2C%20Mexico%2C%20St.%20Lucia%2C%20St.%20Vincent%2C%20Belize%2C%20and%20Turks%20and%20Caicos%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdreamoverwater.com%2Fplaces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDream%20Overwater%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20bungalow's%20deck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd18d2f533b039a883b3e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20bungalow's%20deck.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithout%20a%20desire%20to%20spend%2026%20hours%20traveling%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20I%20settled%20on%20Belize%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20were%20planning%20a%20scuba%20diving%20trip.%20We%20wanted%20to%20go%20somewhere%20with%20incredible%20diving%20but%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20vacation%20on%20a%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20landed%20on%20Belize%2C%20which%20involved%20two%20three-hour%20flights%20from%20Denver%2C%20Colorado.%20If%20we%20had%20flown%20directly%2C%20it%20would've%20taken%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8eaa6bb2a2cbfb48212b8954c9ee8e888e18fba87daa4a2b924d017d323a8b07%26postID%3D65e201f7e3dcaf02712bbef8%26postSlug%3Doverwater-bungalow-experience-belize-inspired-by-maldives-tahiti-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.southwest.com%252Fair%252Fbooking%252Fselect.html%253FadultPassengersCount%253D1%2526fareType%253DUSD%2526passengerType%253DADULT%2526tripType%253Droundtrip%2526departureTimeOfDay%253DALL_DAY%2526returnTimeOfDay%253DALL_DAY%2526reset%253Dtrue%2526returnDate%253D2024-04-02%2526departureDate%253D2024-03-30%2526originationAirportCode%253DDEN%2526destinationAirportCode%253DBZE%2526int%253DLFMASEORTEDENtoBZEBookNow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efour%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20accommodations%2C%20I%20started%20looking%20at%20luxury%20options.%20Thatch%20Caye's%20overwater%20bungalows%20caught%20my%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20I%20could%20have%20the%20overwater%20bungalow%20experience%20much%20closer%20to%20home%20than%20I%20originally%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20private%20island%20is%20home%20to%20eight%20overwater%20bungalows%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20resorts%20that%20offer%20them%20in%20Belize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20are%20considered%20premier%20with%20private%20decks%3B%20the%20other%20three%20share%20a%20deck.%20Depending%20on%20the%20season%2C%20the%20premier%20overwater%20bungalows%20cost%20about%20%24950%20a%20night%20for%20two%20people%2C%20which%20includes%20resort%20fees%20and%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20photos%20online%20were%20stunning.%20Wooden%20decks%20led%20out%20to%20the%20ocean%2C%20and%20each%20premier%20bungalow%20had%20a%20hammock%20for%20lounging%20and%20comfy%20beds%20for%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20say%20settled%2C%20I%20mean%20we%20eagerly%20booked%20two%20nights%20at%20Thatch%20Caye.%20BI%20received%20a%20media%20rate%20for%20the%20two-night%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225254%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20birds-eye%20view%20of%20the%20Thatch%20Caye%20resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cd1966f533b039a883b42e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bird's-eye%20view%20of%20the%20Thatch%20Caye%20resort.%3Cp%3EMuy'Ono%20Resorts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bungalows%20exceeded%20my%20tropical%20vacation%20dreams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20nights%2C%20I%20did%20exactly%20what%20I%20had%20dreamed%20of.%20I%20went%20to%20sleep%20under%20a%20spattering%20of%20night%20stars%20with%20the%20ocean%20lapping%20beneath%20me.%20I%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20wind%20rustling%20in%20the%20thatched%20roof%20and%20the%20sun%20shining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overwater%20bungalows%20lacked%20two%20amenities%20I%20had%20hoped%20for%3A%20a%20clear%20floor%20to%20peer%20into%20the%20ocean%20and%20direct%20water%20access%20from%20my%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20resort%20made%20up%20for%20it%20in%20other%20ways.%20The%20island%20had%20a%20sandy%20beach%20area%20where%20guests%20could%20wade%20in%20the%20water%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20snorkeling%20area%20for%20spotting%20rays%2C%20starfish%2C%20and%20nurse%20sharks.%20There%20were%20complimentary%20kayaks%2C%20paddleboards%2C%20and%20sailboats%2C%20and%20an%20on-site%20dive%20shop%20that%20coordinated%20dives%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20explore%20the%20Belize%20Barrier%20Reef.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Thatch%20Caye%20is%20home%20to%20only%2030%20guests%2C%20the%20entire%20trip%20felt%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbelize-resort-changed-opinion-on-all-inclusive-stays-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20intimate%20than%20other%20all-inclusives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20bonded%20with%20other%20vacationers%20as%20we%20dined%20at%20a%20communal%20dinner%20table%20each%20evening%2C%20and%20I%20watched%20sunsets%20from%20a%20hanging%20hammock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20overwater%20bungalow%20stay%20reminded%20me%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20hop%20on%20an%20all-day%20flight%20to%20experience%20the%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20places%20like%20Tahiti%20are%20no%20longer%20on%20my%20radar.%20And%20Ke