C%20thicker%20layer%20of%20pocket%20coils.%20Durable%20support%20foam%20makes%20up%20the%20bottom%20layer.%20It%20has%20a%20soft%20knit%20cover%20for%20breathability.%20The%20foams%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2Fwhat-is-certified-foam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPUR-US-certified%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20mattress%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2Fservices%2Ful-greenguard-certification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreenguard%20Gold-certified%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tuft%20%26amp%3B%20Needle%20Hybrid%20failed%20the%20bowling%20ball%20test%2C%20but%20the%20motion%20isolation%20wasn't%20awful.%20I%20could%20feel%20the%20motion-dampening%20properties%20while%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20and%20I%20recorded%20impressively%20low%20vibrometer%20readings%20when%20dropping%20the%20bowling%20ball.%20When%20paired%20with%20its%20decent%20edge%20support%2C%20this%20mattress%20is%20great%20for%20couples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hassle-free%20setup%20process%20took%20less%20than%20five%20minutes.%20While%20it%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20bed%20smell%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20dissipated%20by%20bedtime.%20At%20112%20pounds%2C%20this%20is%20a%20heavy%20mattress%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20flop%20around%2C%20making%20it%20a%20little%20easier%20to%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress%5C%22%3Ebest%20cooling%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%20for%20more%20breathable%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20heavy%20people%3A%20Big%20Fig%20Mattress%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221467%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Big%20Fig%20mattress%20on%20a%20bed%20frame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F621d42febea1240018a9084e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHeavier%20individuals%20will%20appreciate%20how%20the%20Big%20Fig%20Mattress%20sinks%20just%20enough%20to%20keep%20one's%20spine%20aligned%20while%20still%20providing%20adequate%20support.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHeavier%20side%20sleepers%2C%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EType%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHybrid%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirmness%20(1%20softest%20to%2010%20firmest)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E7%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20period%20and%20warranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E120%20nights%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E20%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOutstanding%20edge%20support%2C%20good%20heat%20dissipation%2C%20sound%20motion%20isolation%2C%20long%20warranty%2C%201%2C100-pound%20weight%20capacity%2C%20above-average%20firmness%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMay%20not%20be%20comfortable%20for%20lightweight%20side%20sleepers%2C%20hard%20to%20lift%20and%20move%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Big%20Fig%20Mattress%20can%20support%201%2C100%20pounds%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20foundation%20that%20holds%201%2C200%20pounds.%20The%20mattress%20is%20firmer%20than%20average%2C%20making%20it%20the%20best%20mattress%20for%20heavier%20side%20sleepers%20since%20it%20lets%20you%20sink%20in%20enough%20to%20keep%20your%20spine%20aligned%20while%20still%20feeling%20supported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setup%20took%20some%20effort%20since%20the%20Big%20Fig%20weighs%20more%20than%20most%20mattresses.%20I%20recommend%20airing%20the%20bed%20out%20before%20sleeping%20on%20it%2C%20as%20the%20initial%20odor%20took%20a%20day%20to%20dissipate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Big%20Fig%20comprises%20three%20layers%20of%20CertiPUR-US%20certified%20foams%20to%20promote%20durability%2C%20edge%20support%2C%20and%20airflow.%20It%20gets%20more%20durability%20and%20support%20from%20the%20individually%20wra