3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7838dce7f1785b2e690d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sylvester%20Comprehensive%20Cancer%20Center%20in%20Miami%3Cp%3EUniversity%20of%20Miami%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ken%20Griffin%20name%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20philanthropic%20leadership%20that%20drives%20value%20in%20the%20communities%20in%20which%20he%20operates%2C%26quot%3B%20Stuart%20A.%20Miller%2C%20the%20board%20chair%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Miami%20Health%20System%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BMiami%20is%20privileged%20and%20fortunate%20to%20now%20call%20Ken%20Griffin%20one%20of%20our%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-gifts-50-million-university-of-miami-cancer-center-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709671681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e76f15ce7f1785b2e67b2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-gifts-50-million-university-of-miami-cancer-center-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Citadel%20founder's%20gift%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Miami's%20cancer-research%20center%20comes%20after%20he%20pledged%20to%20pause%20giving%20to%20Harvard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22twhite%40insider.com%20(Tiara%20White)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-gifts-50-million-university-of-miami-cancer-center-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saibaba%20Acquittal%3A%20From%20Lack%20of%20Sanction%20to%20Dodgy%20Evidence%2C%20High%20Court%20Judgment%20Tears%20Into%20State's%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2Fsai2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20its%20detailed%20judgment%20acquitting%20former%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20G.N.%20Saibaba%20and%20five%20others%20of%20%E2%80%98terrorism%E2%80%99%20charges%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20has%20virtually%20shredded%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20the%20six%20to%20pieces.%20Noting%20that%20fatal%20violations%20occurred%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20sanction%20to%20prosecute%20was%20granted%20%E2%80%93%20a%20key%20statutory%20safeguard%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20draconian%20terrorism%C2%A0%20law%20%E2%80%93%20the%20court%20also%20rejected%20key%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20prosecution%20in%20the%20case%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20were%20not%20supported%20by%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20293-%20page%20judgment%20which%20describes%20the%20trial%20court%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98guilty%E2%80%99%20verdict%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfailure%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D%20was%20uploaded%20by%20the%20court%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20March%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Justice%20Vinay%20G.%20Joshi%20and%20Justice%20Valimiki%20S.%20Menezes%20acquitted%20Saibaba%2C%20along%20with%20journalist%20Prashant%20Rahi%2C%20Mahesh%20Tikri%2C%20Hem%20Keshwdatta%20Mishra%20and%20Vijay%20Nan%20Tikri%20of%20all%20charges.%20The%20sixth%20person%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Pandu%20Narote%2C%20died%20in%20August%202022%2C%20awaiting%20this%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20claimed%20the%20accused%20were%20members%20of%20the%20banned%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist)%20and%20charged%20them%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20In%202017%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20convicted%20the%20six%20and%20sentenced%20Saibaba%20to%20life%20while%20the%20others%20were%20handed%20down%2010%20year%20sentences.%20Most%20of%20them%20have%20spent%20nearly%20a%20decade%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAPA%20mandates%20a%20two-layered%20sanction%20process%20before%20a%20court%20can%20put%20a%20person%20on%20trial.%20This%20involves%20clearance%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%E2%80%9D%20authority%20as%20well%20as%20the%20sanctioning%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20was%20the%20sixth%20and%20last%20person%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20trial%20court%20framed%20charges%20under%20UAPA%20against%20Saibaba%20on%20February%2021%2C%202015%20even%20though%20the%20order%20sanctioning%20his%20prosecution%20was%20issued%20only%20on%20April%206%2C%202015.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20well%20before%20the%20sanctioning%20authority%E2%80%99s%20mandatory%20clearance%2C%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20the%20charges%20against%20Saibaba%2C%20framed%20its%20charges%20and%20even%20gone%20on%20to%20record%20evidence%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20authority%20did%20not%20apply%20mind%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20other%20five%20persons%2C%20the%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20while%20the%20official%20sanction%20granted%20was%20in%20order%2C%20the%20independent%20authority%E2%80%99s%20report%20which%20preceded%20it%20was%20not.%C2%A0%20The%20independent%20authority%20is%20required%20to%20assess%20the%20material%20evidence%20against%20the%20accused%20persons%20and%20give%20her%20opinion%20before%20the%20sanctioning%20authority%20finally%20grants%20sanction%20for%20prosecution.%20But%20the%20judges%20had%20serious%20objections%20to%20the%20way%20the%20process%20played%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20independent%20authority%20in%20this%20case%20was%20Vidya%20Gundecha%2C%20the%20then%20director%20of%20prosecution.%20The%20high%20court%20pointed%20to%20section%2045(2)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccreates%20a%20statutory%20bar%20on%20grant%20of%20sanction%20unless%20independent%20authority%20%E2%80%98reviews%E2%80%99%20the%20evidence%20gathered%20and%20gives%20its%20recommendation%20in%20a%20time%20bound%20manner%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CRecommendations%20of%20an%20independent%20authority%20are%20not%20an%20empty%20formality%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20observed.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20however%2C%20Gundecha%20had%20merely%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20against%20the%20arrested%20and%20non-arrested%20accused%20persons%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20recommended%20that%20sanction%20be%20accorded%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Gundecha%E2%80%99s%20non-reasoned%20recommendation%20%E2%80%9Ccryptic%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20court%20said%20that%20her%20act%20(or%20lack%20of%20it%20in%20this%20case)%20has%20frustrated%20the%20law%E2%80%99s%20object.%20A%20cryptic%20communication%20cannot%20be%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%9Creport%E2%80%9D%20as%20expected%20under%20the%20law%2C%20the%20judgment%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%2C%20represented%20by%20senior%20counsel%20Aabad%20Ponda%2C%20had%20argued%20that%20there%20is%20no%20set%20format%20in%20which%20the%20recommendation%20can%20be%20made.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20court%20observed%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20regard%20to%20the%20language%20used%20under%20Sub-clause%20(2)%2C%20though%20the%20reasons%20are%20not%20required%2C%20but%20the%20independent%20authority%20is%20certainly%20expected%20to%20at%20least%20communicate%20in%20brief%20as%20to%20what%20prompted%20the%20authority%20to%20make%20the%20recommendation.%20It%20was%20an%20important%20facet%20of%20the%20process%20of%20sanction%20which%20has%20to%20be%20passed%20to%20the%20Sanctioning%20Authority%20to%20enable%20it%20to%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision.%20We%20do%20agree%20that%20statute%20has%20not%20prescribed%20any%20format%20or%20a%20form%20in%20which%20the%20report%20is%20to%20be%20made.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20the%20minimum%20expectation%20from%20the%20Authority%20that%20the%20report%20would%20convey%20due%20application%20of%20mind.%20The%20very%20purpose%20was%20to%20provide%20assistance%20to%20the%20Sanctioning%20Authority.%20In%20turn%2C%20besides%20a%20go-ahead%20signal%20of%20the%20authority%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20before%20the%20Sanctioning%20Authority%20for%20its%20consideration%20while%20granting%20sanction.%20As%20such%20the%20legislative%20object%20has%20been%20completely%20frustrated%20by%20said%20communication%20which%20was%20not%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20additional%20filter%20provided%20by%20the%20statute.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20defence%20counsel%20Subodh%20Dharmadhikari%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20Saibaba%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20legal%20history%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20the%20amendments%20which%20had%20been%20made%20to%20the%20law.%20Since%20the%20law%20was%20stringent%2C%20Dharmadhikari%20said%20that%20it%20provided%20various%20safeguards%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20power%20to%20arrest%20and%20search.%20He%20argued%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA1967-37.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esection%2045%20of%20UAPA%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20unique%20provision%20which%20added%20a%20very%20important%20pre-cognizance%2C%20presanction%20filter%20to%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20sanction%20provision%20goes%20to%20the%20root%20of%20this%20case%2C%20and%20has%20virtually%20raised%20doubts%20over%20the%20entire%20trial%2C%20the%20high%20court%20observed%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20total%20non-compliance%20with%20the%20sanction%20provision%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20very%20root%20of%20the%20case%2C%20vitiating%20everything%20against%20accused%20No.6%20(Saibaba)%20from%20its%20inception%20for%20want%20of%20authority%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20to%20proceed.%20In%20sum%20and%20substance%2C%20the%20prosecution%20against%20accused%20No.6%20G.N.%20Saibaba%20for%20want%20of%20valid%20sanction%20is%20also%20totally%20vitiated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20defence%20team%20systematically%20built%20its%20argument%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Ponda%20contended%20that%20the%20issue%20of%20sanction%20was%20not%20raised%20by%20the%20defence%20at%20the%20time%20of%20framing%20of%20charges%20or%20at%20other%20important%20stages%20of%20the%20trial%20so%20it%20could%20not%20be%20brought%20up%20now.%20The%20defence%20responded%20by%20bringing%20the%20bail%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20accused%20way%20back%20in%20June%202014%20where%20the%20issue%20of%20sanction%20was%20raised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20simply%20a%20%E2%80%98technical%E2%80%99%20error%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20prosecution%20insisted%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20sanction%20was%20at%20best%20a%20%E2%80%98technical%E2%80%99%20glitch%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20could%20be%20overlooked%20%E2%80%93%20the%20court%20rejected%20this%20argument.%20It%20observed%20that%20while%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F338903%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESection%20465%20of%20the%20Code%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(CrPC)%20does%20allow%20an%20%E2%80%9Cerror%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cirregularity%E2%80%9D%20in%20grant%20of%20sanction%20to%20be%20cured%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20cover%20omission%20or%20total%20absence%20of%20sanction%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20view%2C%20there%20is%20total%20non-compliance%20of%20various%20provisions%20of%20UAPA.%20The%20sanction%20accorded%20to%20prosecute%20Accused%20Nos.1%20to%205%20is%20invalid.%20Taking%20cognizance%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20without%20valid%20sanction%20or%20no%20sanction%20to%20prosecute%20accused%20No.6%20G.N.%20Saibaba%20goes%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20case%2C%20which%20renders%20the%20entire%20proceedings%20null%20and%20void%E2%80%A6%20We%20hold%20that%20the%20trial%20held%20despite%20violation%20of%20mandatory%20provisions%20of%20law%20itself%20amounts%20to%20failure%20of%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20sanction%20aspect%2C%20the%20court%20also%20took%20an%20independent%20look%20at%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20witnesses%20who%20deposed%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20prosecution%20case%20was%20entirely%20built%20on%20the%20statements%20of%2023%20witnesses%2C%20comprising%20only%20police%20personnel%20and%20%3Cem%3Epanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20witnesses.%20The%20court%20also%20looked%20at%20the%20three%20seizures%E2%80%94primarily%20electronic%20evidence%E2%80%94that%20the%20prosecution%20relied%20on%20to%20prove%20its%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20no%20offence%20was%20shown%20to%20be%20committed%20or%20arms%20recovered%20from%20either%20of%20the%20six%20persons%20convicted%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20prosecution%20had%20relied%20upon%20section%2043%20(E)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20which%20allows%20%E2%80%9Cpresumption%E2%80%9D%20of%20an%20offence%20to%20be%20committed.%20The%20section%2C%20however%2C%20can%20be%20applied%20only%20if%20the%20accused%20were%20booked%20section%2015%20and%20subsequently%20punished%20under%20section%2016%20(i.e.%20for%20terrorist%20acts)%20or%20found%20to%20be%20in%20possession%20of%20arms%20or%20explosives.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20neither%20were%20arms%20recovered%20nor%20were%20any%20of%20them%20booked%20under%20section%2015%20or%2016%20of%20the%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6In%20criminal%20jurisprudence%2C%20it%20is%20a%20well-recognised%20principle%20that%20the%20onus%20of%20proof%20lies%20on%20the%20prosecution%20and%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20mere%20preponderance%20of%20probability.%20The%20prosecution%20is%20under%20an%20obligation%20to%20establish%20the%20guilt%20of%20the%20accused%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProsecution%20fails%20to%20provide%20evidence%20to%20back%20up%20charges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20examined%20witness%20statements%20and%20the%20electronic%20evidence%20the%20police%20said%20it%20had%20seized%20but%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20the%20prosecution%20had%20failed%20to%20make%20out%20a%20credible%20case.%20Referring%20to%20video%20footage%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20court%20noted%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%20286%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20electronic%20evidence%20is%20produced%20in%20the%20form%20of%20printed%2Fhard%20copies%20of%20the%20content%20stored%20in%20digital%20form%20or%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20video%20footage%2C%20no%20evidence%20has%20been%20led%20by%20any%20witness%20identifying%20the%20various%20persons%20in%20these%20videos%2C%20or%20deposing%20as%20to%20the%20specific%20statements%20made%20by%20such%20persons%20and%20quoting%20them%2C%20or%20how%20these%20statements%20or%20actions%20in%20videos%20constitute%20material%20to%20make%20out%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20Act.%20Playing%20several%20videos%20or%20requesting%20the%20Court%20to%20read%20through%20hundreds%20of%20pages%20of%20literature%20does%20not%20constitute%20evidence.%20In%20our%20opinion%2C%20there%20should%20have%20been%20specific%20evidence%20led%20through%20witnesses%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20making%20out%20of%20an%20offence.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20depositions%20to%20this%20effect%2C%20we%20are%20afraid%20we%20cannot%20consider%20all%20this%20footage%20to%20be%20evidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%20291%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20clear%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20acquit%20Saibaba%20and%20the%20others%20was%20not%20just%20on%20account%20of%20the%20failure%20to%20grant%20sanction%20to%20prosecute%2C%20the%20judgment%20notes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20prosecution%20has%20failed%20to%20establish%20legal%20arrest%20and%20seizure%20from%20accused%20Nos.1%20to%205%2C%20and%20failed%20to%20establish%20the%20seizure%20of%20incriminating%20material%20from%20the%20house%20search%20of%20accused%20No.6%20G.N.%20Saibaba.%20The%20prosecution%20has%20also%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20electronic%20evidence%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%20292%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20above%20conclusion%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20common%20judgment%20rendered%20by%20the%20Trial%20Court%20%E2%80%A6is%20not%20sustainable%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaibaba%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20jailed%20in%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Saibaba%E2%80%99s%20defence%20in%20the%20trial%20court%20was%20handled%20by%20the%20Nagpur-based%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20who%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20trial%2C%20was%20himself%20arrested%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case.%20Arrested%20on%20June%206%2C%202018%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20be%20incarcerated.%20Gadling%20and%20other%20defence%20lawyers%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20have%20said%20that%20he%20was%20targeted%20mainly%20because%20he%20had%20defended%20Saibaba%20in%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709671262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2Fsai2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsaibaba-acquittal-from-lack-of-sanction-to-dodgy-evidence-high-court-judgment-tears-into-states-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20prosecution%20has%20failed%20to%20establish%20the%20seizure%20of%20incriminating%20material%20from%20the%20house%20search%20of%20G.N.%20Saibaba%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judges%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20prosecution%20has%20also%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20electronic%20evidence%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsaibaba-acquittal-from-lack-of-sanction-to-dodgy-evidence-high-court-judgment-tears-into-states-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reddit's%20power%20users%20can%20buy%20into%20its%20IPO%20through%20a%20directed%20share%20program.%20Here's%20how%20DSPs%20work.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-directed-share-program-dsp-ipo-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20answer%20readers'%20investing%20questions%20and%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting-rating-methodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20how%20we%20assess%20investing%20products%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Paid%20non-client%20promotion%3A%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20we%20receive%20a%20commission%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20opinions%20are%20always%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222050%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22worms-eye%20shot%20of%20people%20with%20colorful%20phones%20in%20a%20circle%20and%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e635b2ce7f1785b2e620ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221025%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20Reddit%20users%20will%20have%20access%20to%20its%20shares%20at%20the%20IPO%20price.%3Cp%3EXavier%20Lorenzo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECompanies%20with%20upcoming%20IPOs%20can%20offer%20directed%20share%20programs%20to%20qualifying%20groups%20of%20retail%20investors%20to%20buy%20IPO%20stock.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEligible%20investors%20must%20receive%20an%20invite%20from%20the%20company%20to%20participate%2C%20as%20shares%20are%20limited.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReddit%20is%20inviting%20select%20users%20and%20moderators%20to%20participate%20in%20its%20offer%20to%20buy%20company%20stock%20in%20March%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3EHoping%20to%20get%20in%20on%20Reddit's%20initial%20public%20offering%3F%20Unless%20you're%20a%20big%20investor%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20unless%20you%20are%20among%20a%20select%C2%A0group%20of%20power%20users%20on%20the%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3E%3Cs%3E%3C%2Fs%3ENon-employed%20forum%20moderators%20and%20users%20(aka%20Redditors)%20can%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20Reddit's%20IPO%20at%20the%20same%20price%20as%20institutional%20investors%20through%20what's%20known%20as%20a%20directed%20share%20program.%20Reddit%20has%20started%20inviting%20Redditors%20meeting%20certain%20moderators%20or%20user%20criteria%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20is%20seeking%20a%20valuation%20of%20up%20to%20%246.5%20billion%20for%20its%20much-anticipated%20IPO%20after%20filing%20to%20go%20public%20on%20February%2022.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20first%20major%20tech%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-ipo%5C%22%3EIPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202024.%20The%20company%20is%20targeting%20a%20price%20range%20of%20%2431%20to%20%2434%20per%20share.%20Typically%2C%20only%20large%20institutional%20investors%20are%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20IPOs%20directly.%20Directed%20share%20programs%20like%20Reddit's%20allow%20companies%20to%20allocate%20shares%20to%20stakeholders%20who%20might%20otherwise%20miss%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESee%20Business%20Insider's%20picks%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%3Ebest%20online%20brokerages%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3E%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20attempt%20at%20engagement%20and%20trying%20to%20translate%20users%20of%20the%20platform%20into%20owners%20of%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Will%20McDonough%2C%20chairman%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corestonecapital.com%2F%5C%22%3ECorestone%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BReddit%20is%20trying%20to%20activate%20its%20user%20base%20to%20become%20equity%20holders%20and%20therefore%20have%20a%20greater%20vested%20interest%20in%20the%20platform's%20success%20so%20that%20they%20continue%20to%20contribute%20to%20it.%20It's%20kind%20of%20like%20buying%20them%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20to%20pre-register%20is%20March%205%2C%20and%20Reddit%20plans%20to%20start%20trading%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20using%20the%20ticker%20symbol%20RDDT%20on%20March%2011.%20Reddit%20Employees%20will%20also%20be%20eligible%20to%20start%20selling%20shares%20at%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EDirected%20share%20programs%20(DSP)%20are%20offered%20by%20companies%20going%20public%20so%20that%20individual%20investors%20can%20access%20company%20shares%20at%20the%20same%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2024-tech-ipos-discord-reddit-chime-stripe-klarna-2023-12%5C%22%3EIPO%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20and%20institutions.%20Rather%20than%20investing%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-a-brokerage-account%5C%22%3Ea%20brokerage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eligible%20retail%20investors%20purchase%20shares%20directly%20from%20the%20company%20or%20business.%20DSPs%20typically%20involve%20restrictions%20on%20who%20can%20participate%2C%20the%20number%20of%20shares%20available%2C%20and%20the%20holding%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20is%20a%20directed%20share%20program%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20a%20directed%20share%20program%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20directed%20share%20program%20(DSP)%20is%20an%20invitation-only%20program%20offered%20by%20companies%20going%20public%20so%20that%20a%20select%20group%20of%20investors%20gets%20access%20to%C2%A0shares%20at%20the%20IPO%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20buying%20shares%20through%20a%20broker%2C%20a%20directed%20share%20program%20allows%20investors%20to%20buy%20IPO%20stock%20directly%20from%20the%20company.%20Only%20people%20the%20company%20invites%20can%20participate%20in%20directed%20share%20programs.%20Usually%2C%20this%20involves%20specific%20regulatory%20restrictions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20number%20of%20shares%20an%20investor%20can%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20may%20offer%20a%20directed%20share%20program%20to%20employees%2C%20vendors%2C%20or%2C%20in%20Reddit's%20case%2C%20loyal%20users%20and%20moderators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternal%20teams%2C%20such%20as%20employees%2C%20are%20inherently%20vested%20in%20the%20success%20of%20a%20platform%20because%20their%20paycheck%20and%20healthcare%20are%20dependent%20on%20it.%20Whereas%20an%20independent%20user%20who%20leverages%20the%20platform%20remains%20to%20be%20proven%20whether%20or%20not%20they%20actually%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonough%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20blow%20up%20in%20the%20company's%20face%20or%20be%20a%20legendary%20story%20of%20commuting%20users.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20isn't%20the%20first%20tech%20company%20to%20use%20directed%20share%20programs.%20In%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fabnb-stock%5C%22%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20US%20individuals%20who%20hosted%20guests%20during%202019%20and%202020%20access%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20company's%20IPO%20through%20a%20DSP%20at%20%2468%20per%20share.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fuber-stock%5C%22%3EUber%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20offered%20a%20DSP%20when%20it%20went%20public%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fairbnb-ipo-stock-offering-price-filing-abnb-trading-debut-nasdaq-2020-12-1029879403%5C%22%3EAirbnb's%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%202020%2C%20successfully%20selling%2051%20million%20shares%20and%20raising%20%243.5%20billion.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20day%2C%20high%20demand%20increased%20the%20stock%20price%20by%20140%25%2C%20reaching%20%24144.71%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-reasons-why-uber-had-such-a-terrible-ipo-2019-5%5C%22%3EUber's%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20less%20successful%20as%20the%20stock%20immediately%20decreased%20from%20its%20initial%20target%20of%20%2445%20per%20share%20and%20opened%20at%20%2442%20per%20share.%20With%20a%20target%20valuation%20ranging%20from%20%2480%20billion%20to%20%2490%20billion%2C%20it%20offered%20180%20million%20shares%2C%20raising%20only%20%248.1%20billion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20an%20IPO%20depends%20on%20the%20public's%20opinion%20of%20the%20company%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20shares%2C%20and%20investor's%20confidence.%20For%20example%2C%20Airbnb%20went%20public%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020%20as%20people%20were%20desperate%20to%20travel%2C%20and%20vaccines%20for%20COVID-19%20had%20just%20been%20announced.%20Whereas%2C%20for%20Uber's%20IPO%2C%20investor%20confidence%20in%20drive-sharing%20apps%20was%20low%20following%20Lyft's%20rough%20IPO%20launch%20less%20than%20two%20months%20prior.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20DSPs%20can%20be%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20regular%20people%20to%20access%20shares%20that%20would%20otherwise%20only%20be%20available%20to%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20and%20institutional%20investors.%20However%2C%20investing%20in%20an%20IPO%20comes%20with%20risk%2C%20so%20only%20those%20with%20a%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsafe-investments%5C%22%3Erisk%20tolerance%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20participate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20a%20directed%20share%20program%20works%5C%22%3EHow%20a%20directed%20share%20program%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20with%20an%20IPO%2C%20a%20certain%20portion%20of%20shares%20are%20set%20aside%20for%20key%20stakeholders%20and%20specific%20high-net-worth%20individuals.%20Directed%20share%20programs%20work%20the%20same%20way.%20During%20the%20underwriting%20process%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20shares%20is%20set%20aside%20for%20a%20designated%20group%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20often%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20IPO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20only%20participate%20in%20a%20company's%20directed%20share%20program%20if%20invited.%20You%20must%20place%20a%20conditional%20buy%20order%20on%20a%20specified%20number%20of%20shares.%20But%20it%20won't%20go%20through%20until%20it%20becomes%20a%20buy%20order%20and%20becomes%20allocated%20to%20your%20account%20until%20the%20company's%20registration%20becomes%20effective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConditional%20orders%20can%20be%20modified%20until%20they%20become%20buy%20orders.%20Once%20they%20become%20buy%20orders%2C%20you're%20obligated%20to%20purchase.%20However%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20you'll%20receive%20your%20requested%20shares.%20The%20number%20of%20available%20shares%20for%20IPOs%20is%20limited%2C%20and%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20your%20hands%20on%20it%20if%20the%20demand%20is%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Risks%5C%22%3EThe%20risk%20involved%20with%20directed%20share%20programs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frisk-vs-volatility%5C%22%3Erisks%3C%2Fa%3E%20associated%20with%20directed%20share%20programs%20is%20that%20a%20DSP%20may%20harm%20the%20company's%20IPO%20by%20causing%20the%20IPO%20value%20to%20inflate.%20Moreover%2C%20if%20many%20DSP%20participants%20start%20to%20sell%20their%20shares%20immediately%20after%20the%20IPO%2C%20the%20stock%20price%20could%20drop%20sharply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonough%20points%20out%20the%20risk%20of%20something%20like%20that%20happening%20with%20Reddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20years%2C%20Reddit%20has%20been%20private%20and%20illiquid.%20Now%2C%20suddenly%2C%20shareholders%20can%20sell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20becomes%20selling%20pressure%20that%20has%20to%20be%20offset%20by%20market%20demand.%20And%20that%20market%20demand%20has%20to%20come%20from%20equity%20holders%20who%20are%20believing%20the%20growth%20story.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20purchased%20through%20DSP%20often%20require%20buyers%20to%20hold%20the%20stock%20for%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20decreasing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-liquidity%5C%22%3Eliquidity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Reddit%20employees%20are%20allowed%20to%20start%20selling%20shares%20once%20it%20officially%20goes%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20method%20to%20manage%20risk%20in%20your%20investment%20portfolio%20is%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-diversification%5C%22%3Ediversifying%3C%2Fa%3E%20your%20asset%20allocation%20within%20and%20across%20market%20sectors.%20That%20way%2C%20you're%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20subject%20to%20large%20losses%20if%20a%20single%20company%20drops%20in%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20participate%20in%20Reddit's%20DSP%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20participate%20in%20Reddit's%20directed%20share%20program%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20began%20rolling%20out%20directed%20share%20program%20pre-registration%20invitations%20to%20certain%20users%20and%20moderators%20on%20February%2022%2C%202024.%20Redditors%20started%20receiving%20emails%20explaining%20the%20upcoming%20IPO%2C%20how%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20DSP%2C%20and%20additional%20program%20requirements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvitations%20were%20rolled%20out%20to%20three%20groups%20of%20Redditors%20based%20on%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222366%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reddit%20IPO%20pre-registration%20invite%20tier%20chart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e61727ce7f1785b2e60b73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221183%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETier%20chart%20for%20Redditors%20receiving%20DSP%20invitations%20from%20Reddit%3Cp%3EReddit%20website%2Fscreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20karma%20is%20the%20score%20calculated%20by%20a%20Redditor's%20total%20upvotes%20on%20posts%20and%20comments%2C%20minus%20any%20downvotes.%20Reddit%20uses%20this%20score%20to%20determine%20if%20someone%20is%20contributing%20to%20the%20platform%20positively%20and%20to%20prevent%20spam%20accounts%20and%20mayhem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModerators%20with%205000%2B%20mod%20actions%20and%20users%20with%20200k%2B%20karma%20were%20the%20first%20to%20receive%20pre-registration%20invites.%20Mods%20with%20less%20than%20500%20mod%20actions%20and%20users%20with%20karma%20scores%20below%2025k%20did%20not%20receive%20invitations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20IPO%20stock%20will%20be%20distributed%20on%20a%20first-come%2C%20first-served%20basis%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20shares%20is%20limited%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20want%20to%20miss%20your%20chance.%20On%20March%201%2C%20all%20Redditors%20with%20active%20accounts%20created%20on%20or%20before%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20could%20start%20pre-registering%20without%20an%20invitation.%20Remember%2C%20there's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20you'll%20receive%20all%20(or%20any)%20of%20your%20requested%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReddit's%20email%20invitations%20also%20specified%20that%20to%20participate%2C%20you%20must%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBe%20a%20current%20US%20resident%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHave%20a%20valid%20social%20security%20or%20permanent%20resident%20number%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBe%20at%20least%2018%20years%20old%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProvide%20full%20legal%20name%20and%20an%20email%20address%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENot%20be%20a%20current%20or%20former%20Reddit%20employee%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConfirmed%20Redditors%20will%20receive%20an%20email%20from%20Reddit's%20DSP%20Administrator%20(noreply%40redditmail.com)%20asking%20for%20additional%20information%20to%20confirm%20eligibility%20after%20the%20last%20day%20of%20pre-registration%20on%20March%205.%20A%20waitlist%20will%20be%20opened%20if%20pre-registration%20fills%20up%20before%20this%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDirected%20shares%20program%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20can%20Reddit%20users%20participate%20in%20the%20company's%20IPO%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EReddit%20users%20(aka%20Redditors)%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20company's%20IPO%20through%20the%20company's%20directed%20share%20program.%20Qualifying%20users%20and%20moderators%20started%20receiving%20pre-registration%20invitations%20starting%20February%2022.%20On%20March%201%2C%20all%20Reddit%20users%20with%20an%20account%20opened%20on%20or%20before%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20became%20eligible%20to%20request%20shares.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20everyone%20will%20receive%20shares%20due%20to%20possible%20high%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20does%20making%20a%20directed%20share%20purchase%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20purchase%20stock%20through%20a%20directed%20share%20program%2C%20you%20buy%20a%20share%20directly%20from%20the%20company%20rather%20than%20through%20a%20broker.%20First%2C%20you'll%20place%20a%20conditional%20order%20on%20the%20number%20of%20shares%20you%20want%20to%20purchase.%20Once%20the%20company's%20registration%20becomes%20effective%2C%20you're%20order%20will%20become%20buy%20orders%20and%20can%20be%20allocated%20to%20your%20account.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20directed%20share%20programs%20open%20to%20everyone%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDirected%20share%20programs%20are%20only%20available%20to%20a%20select%20group%20of%20people%20the%20company%20deems%20eligible.%20Eligible%20participants%20typically%20must%20receive%20an%20invite%20from%20the%20company%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20direct%20share%20program.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20request%20directed%20share%20program%20shares%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20receive%20an%20invitation%20from%20the%20company%20to%20participate%20in%20their%20directed%20share%20program%2C%20you%20can%20request%20conditional%20shares.%20Once%20the%20company's%20registration%20becomes%20effective%2C%20conditional%20shares%20become%20regular%20buy%20orders%20that%20can%20be%20allocated%20to%20your%20account.%20Depending%20on%20the%20regulations%20involved%20with%20specific%20DSPs%2C%20you%20may%20be%20limited%20to%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20directed%20stock%20purchase%20plans%20good%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDirected%20stock%20purchase%20plans%20are%20a%20good%20way%20for%20individual%20investors%20to%20access%20exclusive%20IPO%20stock%20that%20is%20generally%20only%20available%20to%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20and%20institutions.%20However%2C%20IPO%20stock%20can%20be%20risky%2C%20so%20only%20experienced%20investors%20with%20high-risk%20tolerances%20should%20consider%20participating%20in%20direct%20stock%20purchase%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIs%20Reddit's%20DSP%20worth%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20public%20allows%20companies%20to%20raise%20capital%2C%20enhance%20visibility%2C%20and%20increase%20liquidity.%20But%20these%20efforts%20are%20only%20profitable%20if%20the%20public%20agrees%20with%20the%20company's%20move%20to%20go%20public.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20turning%20users%20into%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20McDonough.%20%26quot%3BNow%20these%20people%20are%20holding%20shares%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don't%20just%20trade%20them%20in%20and%20dump%20them%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20really%20strong%2C%20passionate%20equity%20ownership%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20subreddit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-ipo-redditors-stock-wallstreetbets-meme-2024-2%5C%22%3Er%2FWallStreetBets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%2015%20million%20devoted%20Redditors%20publically%20debating%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20DSP.%20While%20some%20users%20are%20interested%20in%20the%20prospects%20the%20IPO%20has%20to%20offer%2C%20others%20are%20threatening%20to%20short%20Reddit's%20stock%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20declines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-directed-share-program-dsp-ipo-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709671093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e635a8ce7f1785b2e6207c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-directed-share-program-dsp-ipo-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Directed%20share%20programs%20allow%20select%20investors%20to%20buy%20company%20stock%20at%20the%20IPO%20price.%20Here's%20what%20to%20know%20about%20Reddit's%20directed%20share%20program.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tessa%20Campbell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22can