accept%20a%20deal%20as%20talks%20continue%20in%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20US%20military%20made%20its%20second%20airdrop%20of%20aid%20to%20Gaza%2C%20Biden%20also%20told%20ally%20Israel%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bno%20excuses%26quot%3B%20for%20failing%20to%20allow%20more%20aid%20into%20the%20Palestinian%20enclave%20where%20the%20UN%20warns%20famine%20is%20looming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden's%20comments%20came%20as%20US%20frustration%20grows%20both%20with%20Israel%20over%20Gaza's%20aid%20needs%20and%20spiraling%20civilian%20death%20count%2C%20but%20also%20with%20Hamas%20for%20stalling%20on%20conditions%20including%20the%20release%20of%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%2C%2081%2C%20told%20reporters%20as%20he%20flew%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House%20from%20the%20Camp%20David%20presidential%20retreat%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israelis%20have%20been%20cooperating%2C%20the%20offer%20(of%20a%20ceasefire)%20is%20rational.%20We'll%20know%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%20But%20we%20need%20the%20ceasefire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20got%20to%20be%20a%20ceasefire%20because%20Ramadan%20--%20if%20we%20get%20into%20circumstances%20where%20this%20continues%20to%20Ramadan%2C%20Israel%20and%20Jerusalem%20could%20be%20very%2C%20very%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamadan%20will%20start%20on%20March%2010%20or%2011%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20lunar%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20did%20not%20elaborate%2C%20but%20the%20United%20States%20last%20week%20urged%20Israel%20to%20allow%20Muslims%20to%20worship%20at%20the%20flashpoint%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20compound%20in%20Jerusalem%20during%20Ramadan%2C%20after%20a%20far-right%20minister%20proposed%20barring%20Palestinians%20from%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrat%20Biden%20faces%20acute%20political%20pressure%20in%20an%20election%20year%20over%20his%20support%20for%20Israel%20amid%20Gaza's%20soaring%20civilian%20death%20count%2C%20which%20the%20health%20ministry%20there%20has%20put%20at%2030%2C631%2C%20mostly%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20vowed%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%20after%20its%20unprecedented%20October%207%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20around%201%2C160%20people%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20official%20figures%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'No%20excuses'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20separately%20called%20on%20Hamas%20to%20accept%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20with%20Israel%20as%20the%20militants%20met%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators%20in%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20on%20Hamas%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20whether%20it%20is%20prepared%20to%20engage%20in%20that%20ceasefire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20met%20the%20Qatari%20prime%20minister%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Washington%20publicly%20put%20the%20onus%20on%20Hamas%20to%20agree%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20frustrated%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20refusal%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20offensive%20or%20let%20in%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20working%20with%20them%20very%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%2C%20who%20is%20seeking%20reelection%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20get%20more%20aid%20into%20Gaza.%20There's%20no%20excuses%2C%20none.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20cargo%20planes%20airdropped%20more%20than%2036%2C000%20meals%20to%20Gaza%20Tuesday%20in%20a%20joint%20operation%20with%20Jordan%2C%20the%20US%20military%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20second%20such%20operation%20since%20Biden%20gave%20the%20order%20last%20week%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20horrific%20incident%20in%20which%20more%20than%20100%20people%20