the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20six%20for%20the%20NCP%2C%20a%20prospect%20the%20other%20partners%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20-%20as%20the%20alliance%20is%20known%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20%C2%A0are%20not%20happy%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20the%20Sena%20symbol%20and%20name%20are%20with%20him%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Shinde%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20been%20pushing%20to%20be%20allocated%2023%20seats%2C%20the%20same%20number%20that%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20contested%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20-%20before%20the%20split%20in%202022.%20Failing%20that%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20and%20his%20party%20are%20reportedly%20ready%20to%20settle%20for%2018%20seats%2C%20which%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20won%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20division%20of%20constituencies%20with%20the%20then%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20caused%20heartburn%20on%20both%20sides%20even%20in%202019.%20The%20national%20party%20had%20contested%2025%20seats%20and%20won%2023%20while%20the%20Sena%20had%20contested%2023%20and%20won%2018.%20The%20BJP%20camp%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20believes%20it%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20larger%20share%20than%20last%20time%20given%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20popularity%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplicating%20matters%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20entry%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%2C%20which%20joined%20the%20government%20last%20year%20and%20is%20pushing%20for%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20then%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20united%20NCP%20had%20only%20won%20four%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContentious%20Seats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20while%20a%20consensus%20is%20emerging%20on%20most%20other%20seats%2C%2010%20are%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20bone%20of%20contention.%20These%20are%20Kalyan%2C%20South%20Mumbai%2C%20Ratnagiri-Sindhudurg%2C%20Shirur%2C%20Amravati%2C%20Sambhajinagar%20Nagar%2C%20Hingoli%2C%20Nashik%2C%20Ramtek%20and%20Maval%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kalyan%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Shinde's%20son%2C%20Shrikant%20Shinde%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%2C%20but%20the%20local%20unit%20of%20BJP%20wants%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20constituency.%20The%20BJP%20claims%20Kalyan%20is%20a%20traditional%20seat%20of%20the%20party%20which%20it%20had%20given%20to%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%202019%20under%20pressure%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%C2%A0Union%20Minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20had%20also%20conducted%20a%20review%20of%20the%20constituency%20and%20apprised%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Sawant%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20the%20South%20Mumbai%20constituency%20and%20the%20Shinde%20faction%20is%20keen%20to%20contest%20on%20it%20because%20it%20is%20traditionally%20a%20Sena%20seat.%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narvekar%20from%20the%20BJP%20has%2C%20however%2C%20also%20shown%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pune%20district's%20Maval%2C%20Shrirang%20Barne%20from%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP.%20%C2%A0But%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20keen%20on%20this%20seat%20as%20his%20son%2C%20Parth%20Pawar%2C%20had%20lost%20to%20Mr%20Barne%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatnagiri-Sindhadurg%20in%20the%20Konkan%20region%20is%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20seat%20but%20Narayan%20Rane%20claimed%20it%20for%20the%20BJP%20last%20week%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20Strongly%20opposing%20this%2C%20Ramdas%20Kadam%20of%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20had%20asked%20whether%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20eliminate%20every%20party%20and%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShirur%20in%20Pune%20district%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20another%20point%20of%20friction.%20Amol%20Kolhe%20from%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchanrd%20Pawar)%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20and%20the%20seat%20is%20now%20being%20claimed%20by%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%20The%20intent%20to%20beat%20Mr%20Kolhe%20has%20been%20announced%20by%20Mr%20Pawar%20himself%2C%20but%20former%20MP%20Shivaji%20Adhalrao%20Patil%20from%20Mr%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20also%20keen%20on%20throwing%20his%20hat%20in%20the%20ring.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavneet%20Rana%20is%20the%20independent%20MP%20from%20Vidarbha's%20Amravati%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20offered%20the%20constituency%20to%20her%20to%20contest%20on%20its%20ticket.%20The%20Shinde%20Sena's%20Anandrao%20Adsul%2C%20a%20former%20MP%2C%20has%20also%20claimed%20the%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambhaji%20Nagar%20in%20Aurangabad%20is%20the%20lone%20seat%20won%20by%20the%20AIMIM%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Imtiaz%20Jaleel%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP.%20Though%20the%20constituency%20has%20been%20traditionally%20fought%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20plans%20to%20field%20Minister%20Sandeepan%20Bhumre%2C%20the%20BJP%20wants%20it%20for%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Finance%2C%20Bhagwat%20Karad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20seat%20which%20is%20being%20eyed%20by%20all%20three%20members%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20is%20Nashik.%20Hemant%20Godse%20from%20the%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%2C%20but%20the%20NCP%20is%20keen%20on%20fielding%20someone%20from%20Minister%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal's%20family%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20staked%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Aurangabad's%20Hingoli%2C%20Sena's%20Hemant%20Patil%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20and%20had%20offered%20to%20resign%20during%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20protest.%20The%20BJP%20is%20also%2C%20however%2C%20interested%20in%20fielding%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrupal%20Tumane%20of%20the%20Sena%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Ramtek%20in%20Nagpur%20seat%20but%20the%20local%20BJP%20cadre%20want%20the%20constituency%20for%20the%20party.%20They%20are%2C%20however%2C%20willing%20to%20settle%20for%20Mr%20Tumane%20fighting%20on%20a%20BJP%20ticket%2C%20sources%20said.%C2