2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68478831.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68478831.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Looks%20At%20One%20Last%20Step%20To%20End%20Hereditary%20Chieftainship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20enforce%20a%20law%20that%20will%20end%20the%20system%20of%20hereditary%20chieftainship%20in%20the%20hills%20areas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Rajkumar%20Imo%20Singh%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20seeking%20to%20scrap%20the%20chieftainship%20system%20to%20end%20the%20rule%20of%20village%20chiefs%2C%20who%20are%20the%20sole%20leaders%20of%20settlements%20and%20own%20entire%20villages%2C%20and%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20setting%20up%20a%20democratic%20way%20of%20rural%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh's%20statement%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20government%20will%20enforce%20an%20Act%2C%20which%20was%20passed%20in%201967%20to%20abolish%20hereditary%20chieftainship%2C%20Imo%20Singh%20said%20the%20then%20President%20had%20also%20given%20assent%20to%20the%20bill%20in%20June%201967.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20remains%20to%20be%20done%20is%20to%20notify%20the%20Act%20in%20the%20official%20gazette%2C%20government%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20important%20statement%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20that%20the%20state%20government%20will%20consult%20and%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20The%20Manipur%20Hill%20Areas%20(Acquisition%20of%20Chiefs'%20Rights)%20Act%2C%201967.%20This%20Act%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20on%20January%2010%2C%201967%20to%20abolish%20hereditary%20chieftainship%2C%26quot%3B%20Imo%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%20this%20Act%20has%20not%20been%20enforced%20till%20now%2C%20thus%20enabling%20the%20chieftains%20to%20continue%20with%20their%20rights%20and%20establish%20villages%20as%20per%20their%20hereditary%20practices.%20One%20can%20see%20the%20exponential%20growth%20of%20villages%20in%20these%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Imo%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BManipur%20is%20the%20only%20state%20in%20the%20North%20East%20where%20this%20Act%20isn't%20implemented.%20Even%20a%20state%20like%20Mizoram%20had%20implemented%20a%20similar%20act%20for%20abolishing%20chieftainship%20way%20back%20in%201954%20when%20it%20was%20a%20part%20of%20Assam.%20(The)%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20to%20implement%20this%20Act%20at%20the%20earliest%20date%2C%20which%20we%20are%20hopeful%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EA%20very%20important%20statement%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Legislative%20Assembly%20that%20the%20State%20Government%20will%20consult%20and%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20The%20Manipur%20Hill%20Areas%20(Acquisition%20of%20Chiefs'%20Rights)%20Act%201967.%20This%20Act%20was%20passed%20by...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajkumar%20Imo%20Singh%20(%40imosingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimosingh%2Fstatus%2F1764652787504439662%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hereditary%20chieftainship%20system%20has%20faced%20severe%20criticism%20over%20its%20allegedly%20exploitative%20nature%20in%20modern%20times.%20The%20feudal%20system%20often%20leads%20to%20nepotism%20and%20autocracy%20-%20when%20the%20current%20chief%20dies%2C%20only%20his%20son%20can%20become%20the%20next%20chief.%20Power%20struggles%20among%20siblings%20have%20led%20to%20mushrooming%20of%20villages%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20bordering%20Myanmar%20-%20the%20junta%20nation%20that's%20struggling%20for%20its%20own%20survival%20-%20is%20yet%20to%20see%20peace%2010%20months%20after%20violence%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%2C%20who%20follow%20the%20chieftainship%20system%2C%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20over%20serious%20disagreements%20on%20sharing%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20political%20representation%2C%20and%20affirmative%20action%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20clashes%20began%2C%2010%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20have%20been%20asking%20the%20central%20government%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20administration%26quot%3B%20from%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5gl7kf2g_manipur-generic-debanish-credit_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Act%20Not%20Enforced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20Manipur%20never%20enforced%20the%20Act%20to%20scrap%20hereditary%20chieftainship%20for%20decades%20since%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20assembly%20and%20cleared%20by%20the%20President%2C%20state%20government%20sources%20said%20the%20fault%20lies%20with%20successive%20Congress%20governments%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%20ruled%20Manipur%20for%20the%20most%20part%20of%20the%20decades%20since%20Independence.%20Other%20parties%20came%20and%20went%20briefly%2C%20like%20blips%20on%20a%20screen.%20They%20never%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20treat%20the%20deep%20wounds%20inflicted%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20government%20source%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone%20from%20Imphal%2C%20requ