ocial%20media%20for%20not%20conforming%20to%20societal%20norms%20as%20a%20mother.%20She%20defended%20her%20choices%20and%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20staying%20true%20to%20oneself.%20She%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20challenges%20of%20motherhood%20and%20the%20criticism%20she%20faced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcelina-jaitly-shares-a-lengthy-note-on-being-trolled-for-her-breastfeeding-picture-ahead-of-womens-day%2Farticleshow%2F108244719.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UN%20Envoy%20Says%20Hamas%20Likely%20Committed%20Rape%20During%20October%207%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05221908%2FPramila-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20envoy%20who%20focuses%20on%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%20has%20said%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20grounds%E2%80%9D%20to%20believe%20Hamas%20committed%20rape%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-struggles-to-discuss-october-7-sexual-violence%2Fa-67792467%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Csexualised%20torture%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20other%20inhumane%20treatment%20of%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20its%20October%20attack%20in%20southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPramila%20Patten%2C%20who%20visited%20Israel%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%20with%20a%20nine-member%20technical%20team%2C%20said%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20grounds%20to%20believe%20that%20such%20violence%20may%20be%20ongoing%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20came%20to%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatten%20said%2C%20based%20on%20first-hand%20accounts%20of%20released%20hostages%2C%20the%20team%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20clear%20and%20convincing%20information%E2%80%9D%20that%20some%20women%20and%20children%20were%20subjected%20to%20the%20same%20sexual%20violence%20during%20their%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20envoy%20added%20that%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20reasonable%20grounds%20to%20believe%20that%20multiple%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20violence%20took%20place%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%20and%20its%20surroundings%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20victims%20being%20subjected%20to%20rape%20and%2For%20gang%20rape%20and%20then%20killed%20or%20killed%20while%20being%20raped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20further%20accounts%20of%20individuals%20who%20witnessed%20at%20least%20two%20incidents%20of%20rape%20of%20corpses%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patten%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20credible%20sources%20at%20the%20Nova%20music%20festival%20site%20described%20seeing%20multiple%20murdered%20individuals%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%20whose%20bodies%20were%20found%20naked%20from%20the%20waist%20down%2C%20some%20totally%20naked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20some%20had%20been%20shot%20in%20the%20head%2C%20some%20were%20bound%20and%20tied%20to%20trees%20or%20poles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatten%E2%80%99s%20conclusions%20were%20drawn%20from%20witness%20testimony%20and%20circumstantial%20evidence%20which%20she%20said%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20indicative%20of%20some%20forms%20of%20sexual%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20so%20far%20no%20victims%20of%20sexual%20violence%20have%20come%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20envoy%20called%20for%20further%20investigations%2C%20stressing%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20true%20prevalence%20of%20sexual%20violence%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20and%20their%20aftermath%20may%20take%20months%20or%20years%20to%20emerge%20and%20may%20never%20be%20fully%20known%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20comes%20nearly%20five%20months%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20in%20which%20Hamas%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C100%20people%20and%20took%20some%20250%20others%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20said%20it%20believes%20130%20