sters%20must%20contest%2C%20if%20the%20party%20asks%20them%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20reluctance%20is%20palpable%20even%20in%20Telangana%20-%20the%20other%20southern%20state%20where%20the%20Congress%20wrested%20power%20-%20it's%20more%20pronounced%20in%20Karnataka%20where%2C%20since%202004%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20not%20less%20than%2017%20of%2028%20parliamentary%20seats.%20The%20ruling%20party's%20two-decade%20Karnataka%20juggernaut%20hit%20a%20peak%20in%202019%20with%20a%20near%20total%20sweep%20-%2025%20of%20the%2028%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20present%20Congress%20president%2C%20lost%20his%20traditional%20stronghold%20of%20Gulbarga%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202019.%20Other%20strong%20parliamentary%20faces%20like%20KH%20Muniyappa%2C%20a%20seven-time%20MP%20from%20Kolar%2C%20lost%20in%202019%20and%20subsequently%20shifted%20to%20state%20politics%2C%20winning%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%202023.%20He%20now%20seems%20settled%20into%20a%20comfortable%20ministership%20in%20the%20Siddaramiah%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20Congress%20veterans%20who%20held%20out%20till%202019%2C%20but%20the%20real%20problem%20is%20that%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20party%20has%20failed%20to%20nurture%20strong%20young%20parliamentary%20aspirants%20in%20most%20constituencies.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20three%20urban%20seats%20of%20Bengaluru%20(North%2C%20South%20and%20Central)%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20tried%20various%20candidates%20since%202004%2C%20including%20Nandan%20Nilekani%20in%20Bengaluru%20South%20in%202014%2C%20but%20has%20failed%20to%20breach%20the%20BJP%20bastion.%20There%20%C2%A0are%2017%20such%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20had%20consecutive%20wins%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20and%20finding%20candidates%2C%20young%20or%20old%2C%20who%20can%20put%20up%20a%20genuine%20fight%2C%20is%20a%20challenge%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20exactly%20why%20the%20Congress%20wants%20serving%20state%20ministers%20to%20enter%20the%20poll%20contest.%20The%20only%20way%20it%20can%20ensure%20that%20a%20candidate%20puts%20up%20a%20strong%20fight%20is%20if%20it%20becomes%20a%20prestige%20battle.%20For%20instance%2C%20state%20Congress%20chief%20DK%20Shivakumar's%20brother%20DK%20Suresh%20is%20the%20lone%20Congress%20MP%20who%20survived%20the%20BJP%20sweep%20in%202019%2C%20and%20has%20consistently%20held%20the%20Bengaluru%20Rural%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20use%20this%20as%20an%20example%20to%20show%20that%20if%20one%20puts%20up%20a%20genuine%20fight%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20wrest%20a%20seat%20even%20in%20a%20sweep%20election.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20they%20assert%20that%20there%20are%20very%20few%20such%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mandya%2C%20after%20the%20death%20of%20actor-politician%20Ambareesh%2C%20his%20widow%20Sumalatha%20contested%20as%20an%20independent%20backed%20by%20the%20BJP%20because%20the%20Congress%2C%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%2C%20gave%20the%20seat%20to%20its%20ally%20in%202019.%20Since%20then%2C%20Sumalatha%20has%20firmly%20stayed%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20to%20get%20state%20cabinet%20minister%20HC%20Mahadevappa%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20from%20here.%20He%20is%20clearly%20reluctant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20powerful%20state%20leaders%20dive%20into%20the%20contest%20is%20difficult.%20Most%20believe%20that%20it%20could%20weaken%20their%20stature%20if%20they%20lose%20a%20contest%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20spend%20their%20resources.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20I%20win%3F%20will%20I%20give%20up%20ministership%20and%20shift%20to%20Parliament%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20a%20senior%20state%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%20It%20reflects%20the%20thinking%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20given%20that%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana%20were%20the%20only%20two%20seat%20winning%20states%20for%20the%20BJP%20from%20among%20the%20five%20southern%20states%20in%202019%2C%20a%20Congress%20challenge%20here%20is%20essential%20if%20it%20has%20to%20contain%20the%20BJP's%20overall%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20congress%20leader%20from%20Telangana%2C%20who%20was%20once%20a%20parliamentarian%20and%20later%20contested%20and%20lost%20the%202023%20assembly%20polls%2C%20shared%20that%20it's%20too%20expensive%20to%20contest%20a%20parliamentary%20poll.%20It%20was%20better%20to%20look%20for%20entry%20into%20the%20legislative%20council%20and%20be%20active%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20he%20said%2C%20again%20requesting%20anonymity.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20be%20different%20had%20there%20been%20a%20realistic%20chance%20of%20making%20it%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20is%20contesting%20with%20little%20hope%20of%20a%20change%20in%20Delhi.%20Which%20is%20why%20party%20strategists%20feel%20that%20prestige%20battles%20or%20one%20that%20revolves%20around%20political%20rivalry%2Fsurvival%2C%20backed%20by%20strong%20money%20power%20or%20the%20caste%20vote%20could%20be%20crucial%20motivation%20and%20should%20be%20factored%20in%20choosing%20%26quot%3Bwinnable%26quot%3B%20candidates%20in%20states%20like%20Karnataka%20and%20Telangana.%20Even%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20dominant%20Congress%20ally%2C%20the%20DMK%2C%20is%20keen%20to%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20choice%20of%20candidates%20by%20the%20Congress.%20Which%20is%20why%20they%20are%20yet%20to%20firm%20up%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%20In%20fact%2C%202019%20was%20a%20sweep%20for%20the%20DMK-Congress%20alliance%2C%20which%20won%2038%20of%20the%2039%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20lone%20defeat%20was%20the%20then%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Congress%20president%20EVKS%20Elangovan%2C%20who%20lost%20to%20AIADMK%20leader%20O%20Paneerselvam's%20son%20P%20Raveendranath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lesson%20that%20if%20a%20strong%20candidate%20like%20DK%20Suresh%20can%20withstand%20a%20BJP%20onslaught%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20candidate%20who%20doesn't%20work%20on%20the%20ground%20can%20lose%20even%20if%20there's%20a%20sweep%20election%20for%20the%20party.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20Karnataka%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20all%20focussed%20on%20an%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20push.%20The%20issues%20that%20it%20has%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20-%20a%20Temple%20Bill%2C%20alleged%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20and%20a%20scathing%20political%20attack%20on%20the%20state%20government%20after%20the%20Rameshwaram%20cafe%20blast%20-%20clearly%20reveal%20the%20party's%20strategy.%20Hindutva%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20persona%20are%20its%20core%20selling%20points%20this%20time%20and%20there%20is%20lesser%20emphasis%20on%20Karnataka's%20famous%20caste%20and%20sect%20arithmetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20alliance%20with%20the%20JD(S)%20seems%20extraordinarily%20strong%20on%20paper%20and%20the%20vote%20shares%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20put%20together%2C%20since%202004%2C%20is%20comfortably%20above%20the%2050%20percent%20mark.%20This%20is%20an%20enormous%20reality%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20been%20traditionally%20weaker%20in%20any%20%C2%A0parliamentary%20face%20off%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20leadership%20is%20keen%20to%20put%20up%20a%20fight%20and%20it%20is%20a%20prestige%20battle%20for%20the%20Congress%20president.%20It's%20also%20a%20battle%20that%20could%20determine%20the%20road%20ahead%20for%20the%20state%20government%2C%20with%20conflicting%20power%20centres.%20In%20fact%2C%20Siddarmiah's%20son%20Dr.%20Yatheendra%20publicly%20linked%20his%20father's%20continuance%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20the%20party's%20showing%20in%20the%20parliamentary%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objective%20and%20intent%20are%20there%2C%20the%20only%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20have%20candidates%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20take%20the%20fight%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709656440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fjntou0ng_rahul-gandhi-m-kharge_625x300_15_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-finding-strong-karnataka-candidates-is-congress-1st-challenge-5182800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Electoral%20politics%20is%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20largely%20a%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20for%20the%20contestants%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20state%20like%20Karnataka%20with%20India's%20richest%20legislators%20and%20parliamentarians%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20have%20huge%20business%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-finding-strong-karnataka-candidates-is-congress-1st-challenge-5182800%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-finding-strong-karnataka-candidates-is-congress-1st-challenge-5182800%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-finding-strong-karnataka-candidates-is-congress-1st-challenge-5182800%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20times%20Janhvi%20resembled%20her%20mother%20Sridevi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709655730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108244189%2Cimgsize-81664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2F5-times-janhvi-kapoor-resembled-her-iconic-mother-sridevi%2Fphotostory%2F108244189.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220