bollywood%2Fnews%2Fdiljit-dosanjh-hilariously-dubs-kareena-kiara-advani-bill-gates-mark-zuckerberg-and-other-celebs-dancing-on-his-performance-at-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-pre-wedding-celebrations%2Farticleshow%2F108243916.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUsed%20Pitch%20From%20Ranji%26quot%3B%3A%20Bairstow's%20Massive%20Take%20Ahead%20Of%20Dharamsala%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20of%20the%20closely-contested%20series%20between%20India%20and%20England%20slated%20to%20start%20on%20March%207%2C%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20has%20said%20that%20playing%20his%20100th%20long-format%20match%20means%20%26quot%3Bhell%20of%20a%20lot%26quot%3B%20England's%20fifth%20game%20against%20India%20at%20Dharamshala%20will%20mark%20Bairstow's%20100th%20Test%20appearance%20after%20head%20coach%20Brendon%20McCullum%20confirmed%20his%20place%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%20The%2034-year-old%20has%20been%20underwhelming%20in%20the%20series%20as%20he%20has%20amassed%20just%20170%20runs%20in%20four%20Test%20matches.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%2C%20Bairstow%20talked%20about%20the%20pitch%20at%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20and%20said%20that%20it's%20a%20used%20wicket%20from%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20the%20ground%20staff%20for%20doing%20an%20%26quot%3Bamazing%20job%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaying%20100%20Tests%20means%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20lot.%20It's%20a%20used%20pitch%20from%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20last%20month...%20let's%20see.%20Ground%20staff%20have%20done%20an%20amazing%20job%20with%20the%20pitch%20considering%20the%20weather%20we%20have%20had%20here.%20They%20have%20done%20a%20great%20job%20with%20the%20outfield%20here%20in%20Dharamshala.%20Looks%20good.%20The%20ground%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20picturesque%20venues%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%20have%20lost%20three%20matches%20in%20succession%20in%20the%20series%20after%20clinching%20victory%20in%20the%20first%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visitors%20had%20their%20chances%2C%20notably%20in%20Rajkot%20and%20Ranchi%2C%20but%20India%20came%20back%20strong%20on%20both%20occasions%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20England%20still%20have%20World%20Test%20Championship%20points%20to%20gain%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20even%20though%20the%20series%20is%20decided.%20India%20are%20on%20top%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings%20with%20points%20percentage%20of%2064.58%20while%20England%20are%20ranked%20eighth%20on%20points%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709653500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F5n70rafg_sad_625x300_05_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fused-pitch-from-ranji-trophy-jonny-bairstows-bouncer-ahead-of-dharamsala-test-5180289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jonny%20Bairstow%20talked%20about%20the%20pitch%20at%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20and%20said%20that%20it's%20a%20used%20wicket%20from%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Luxury%20hotel%20offers%20free%20night's%20stay%20if%20it%20rains%20too%20much%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709653260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-singapore-rain_6479671.jpg%3F20240305173908%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fluxury-hotel-in-singapore-offers-guests-free-nights-stay-if-it-rains-too-much-13087844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20luxury%20hotel%20is%20offering%20a%20free%20night's%20stay%20to%20guests%20if%20their%20trip%20is%20ruined%20by%20too%20much%20rain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2