20foolish%20to%20make%20a%20biopic%20about%20me%20without%20actually%20involving%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20went%20on%20to%20talk%20about%20being%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bsex%20symbol%26quot%3B%20for%20years%20now%2C%20especially%20men.%20Her%20beautifully%20written%20note%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BQuite%20frankly%2C%20nobody%20knows%20me%20like%20I%20do%20-%20so%20any%20research%20to%20this%20end%20would%20be%20incomplete%2C%20even%20flawed%2C%20without%20my%20input.%20I'd%20wager%20that%20for%20every%20factoid%20about%20me%20that's%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20are%20a%20hundred%20more%20that%20are%20known%20just%20to%20me.%20There%20are%20a%20trove%20of%20milestones%2C%20anecdotes%20and%20personal%20revelations%20that%20are%20integral%20to%20understanding%20my%20journey.%20Oh%2C%20it's%20been%20an%20interesting%20life%20indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20also%20make%20no%20bones%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20I'm%20wary%20of%20my%20story%20being%20told%20by%20strangers.%20Especially%20men.%20The%20%E2%80%9Csex%20symbol%E2%80%9D%20tag%20is%20impossible%20to%20shake%20(believe%20me%2C%20it's%20been%2050%20years)%20and%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20wrong%20storyteller%20may%20well%20devolve%20into%20a%20work%20of%20crass%20voyeurism%20and%20conjecture.%20I'm%20only%20too%20aware%20of%20the%20stereotyping%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbold%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20neither%20a%20seductress%2C%20nor%20a%20damsel%20in%20distress.%20And%20I%20am%20certainly%20not%20a%20victim.%20There%20have%20been%20conversations%20about%20a%20potential%20series%20or%20films%2C%20and%20I'm%20slowly%20warming%20to%20the%20idea.%26quot%3B%20Before%20signing%20of%2C%20the%20actress%20said%20that%20it%20would%20take%2C%20perhaps%20a%20sensitive%20director%2C%20a%20brave%20writer%2C%20an%20immaculate%20cast%20for%20her%20biopic%20to%20come%20to%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20Zeenat%20Aman's%20post%20below%