20the%20two%20women%20saw%20visible%20changes.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20heard%20women%20at%20her%20apartment%20complex%20discuss%20hair%20fall%20problems.%20As%20they%20discussed%20possible%20solutions%2C%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20oil%20emerged%20as%20a%20clear%20winner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother-in-law%2C%20daughter-in-law%20duo%20then%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20help%20women%20at%20their%20apartment%20regain%20their%20long%20locks%20again.%20Starting%20with%20a%20small%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%2C%20the%20response%20pushed%20them%20to%20consider%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20Dua%20launched%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20sells%20hair%20oil%20for%20%E2%80%98hair%20fall%20control%E2%80%99%2C%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub.%20Launched%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20the%20oil%20has%20found%20its%20way%20to%20over%2067%2C000%20homes%2C%20selling%20over%20one%20lakh%20bottles%20and%20earning%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakhs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20this%20story%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20run%20by%20a%20mother%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20helping%20them%20gain%20financial%20freedom%20and%20giving%20wings%20to%20their%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20an%20age%20old%20problem%20faced%20by%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20make%20the%20hair%20oil%20using%2013%20ingredients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%