uced.%20My%20son%2C%20too%2C%20uses%20it%20and%20has%20seen%20good%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kamaljeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20six%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20just%20worked%20on%20fulfilling%20orders.%20There%20would%20be%20oil%20simmering%20on%20the%20gas%20morning%2C%20afternoon%20and%20evening%3B%20with%20its%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20years.%20As%20orders%20crossed%20almost%20300%20per%20day%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20it%20could%20no%20longer%20be%20managed%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20looked%20for%20manufacturing%20facilities.%20They%20had%20a%20caveat%20though%20%E2%80%93%20it%20had%20to%20be%20handmade.%20While%20many%20refused%2C%20they%20found%20one%20in%20Panchkula%2C%20where%20they%20replicated%20the%20setup%2C%20where%20more%20than%2050%20women%20manufacture%20the%20oil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20product%20of%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98anti-hairfall%E2%80%99%20oil%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20499%20for%20a%20100%20ml%20bottle%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20curry%20leaf%20and%20hibiscus%20shampoo%20which%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20449%20for%20a%20200%20ml%20bottle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENidhi%20and%20Rajni%20recently%20moved%20into%20an%20office%20and%20are%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20team.%20The%20two%20mothers%20also%20plan%20to%20launch%20more%20natural%20hair%20care%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20Rajni%20feel%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20an%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%2060s%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20we%20all%20have%20the%20spirit%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20build%20a%20business.%20Age%20is%20no%20bar%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20achieving%20something.%20You%20will%20definitely%20find%20your%20hidden%20