3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Focean-infinity-malaysia-airlines-missing-flight-mh370-b2506995.html%5C%22%3EIndependent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Ocean%20Infinity%2C%20a%20marine%20robotics%20company%20based%20in%20Texas%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Malaysian%20government%C2%A0for%20a%20new%20search%20in%20the%20southern%20Indian%20Ocean%20where%20the%20plane%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20crashed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20chief%20executive%20officer%20Oliver%20Plunkett%20said%2C%20''We%20now%20feel%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20the%20search%20for%20MH370%2C%20and%20have%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Malaysian%20government.%20Finding%20MH370%20and%20bringing%20some%20resolution%20for%20all%20connected%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20aircraft%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20in%20our%20minds%20since%20we%20left%20the%20southern%20Indian%20Ocean%20in%202018.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20focused%20on%20driving%20the%20transformation%20of%20operations%20at%20sea%3B%20innovating%20with%20technology%20and%20robotics%20to%20further%20advance%20our%20ocean%20search%20capabilities%2C''%20Mr%C2%A0Plunkett%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20company%20has%20proposed%20an%20all-new%20no-find%2C%20no-fee%20search.%C2%A0Ocean%20Infinity%20had%20last%20attempted%20to%20find%20the%20missing%20plane%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2Fmalaysia-airlines-flight-mh370-missing-plane-ocean-infinity-370%2F14490516%2F%5C%22%3EABC7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Malaysia's%20transportation%20minister%20says%20he's%20invited%20Ocean%20Infinity%20to%20share%20its%20new%20evidence%20and%20has%20promised%20that%2C%20if%20it's%20credible%2C%20he'll%20push%20to%20greenlight%20a%20new%20search.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20long%20said%20it%20would%20not%20support%20another%20search%20without%20new%20leads%20on%20the%20plane's%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20flight%20MH370%20with%20227%20passengers%20and%2012%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20disappeared%20after%20leaving%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20Airport%20in%20southern%20Malaysia%20en%20route%20to%20Beijing%2C%20China%2C%20on%20March%208%2C%202014.%C2%A0%20A%20nearly%20three-year%20search%20covering%20120%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20found%20hardly%20any%20trace%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20with%20only%20some%20pieces%20of%20debris%20picked%20up.%20Despite%20the%20largest%20search%20in%20aviation%20history%2C%20the%20plane%20has%20never%20been%20found%20and%20the%20operation%20was%20suspended%20in%20January%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20relatives%20of%20passengers%20aboard%20the%20plane%20also%20pushed%20for%20a%20new%20search%20as%20they%20spoke%20of%20enduring%20grief%20and%20the%20struggle%20to%20find%20closure.%C2%A0About%20500%20relatives%20and%20their%20supporters%20gathered%20at%20a%20shopping%20centre%20near%20the%20Malaysian%20capital%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bremembrance%20day%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20many%20visibly%20overcome%20with%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaysian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwar%20Ibrahim%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmalaysian-pm-anwar-ibrahim-says-happy-to-reopen-mh370-search-after-10-years-5172403%5C%22%3Ehe%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20to%20reopen%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20search%20for%20flight%20MH370%20if%20%26quot%3Bcompelling%26quot%3B%20evidence%20emerged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709649660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2Fg6haansk_malaysia-airline-mh370_625x300_25_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-company-claims-to-have-scientific-evidence-in-search-for-missing-flight-mh370-5182122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Flight%20