nsure%20water%20isn't%20just%20a%20luxury%20for%20the%20rich%20who%20can%20afford%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20a%205%2C000-litre%20water%20tanker%20stood%20at%20Rs%20500%20in%20the%20city%20but%20after%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20price%20shot%20up%20to%20Rs%202%2C000.%20Around%204%2C000%20private%20tankers%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20city.%20Out%20of%2014%2C000%20borewells%20approximately%207%2C000%20have%20dried%20up%20leading%20to%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20shortage%20in%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pay%20three%20times%20the%20price%20for%20one%20load%20of%20water%20through%20tankers.%20When%20we%20pay%20Rs%202%2C000%2C%20they%20arrive%20soon.%20When%20we%20negotiate%20to%20Rs%201%2C500%2C%20we%20need%20to%20wait%203-4%20days.%20The%20problem%20is%20only%20worsening%2C%26quot%3B%20Navya%2C%20a%20Bengaluru%20resident%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20warned%20the%20water%20tanker%20owners%20in%20the%20state%20that%20the%20government%20would%20seize%20their%20tankers%20if%20they%20didn't%20register%20with%20the%20authorities%20before%20the%20deadline%20of%20March%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%20total%203%2C500%20water%20tankers%20in%20Bengaluru%20city%2C%20only%2010%20per%20cent%20i.e%20219%20tankers%2C%20have%20registered%20with%20the%20authorities.%20The%20government%20will%20seize%20them%20if%20they%20don't%20register%20before%20the%20deadline%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAround%20Rs%20854%20crore%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20district%20officials%20and%20another%20Rs%2070%20crore%20for%20borewells.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20223%20out%20of%20236%20Taluks%20of%20Karnataka%20are%20reeling%20under%20drought%20among%20them%2C%20219%20are%20badly%20affected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20laid%2