le.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20since%20his%20dissent%20he%20had%20met%20scores%20of%20people%20who%20were%20%E2%80%9Coffended%20by%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20party%20insulted%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20by%20boycotting%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20further%20distract%20and%20humiliate%20this%20pious%20occasion%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20attempted%20to%20create%20ruckus%20in%20Assam%20which%20further%20angered%20our%20party%20cadres%20and%20citizens%20of%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20then%20on%20the%20Assam%20leg%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-rahul-gandhi-stages-sit-in-after-being-stopped-from-visiting-assam-shrine%5C%22%3Estopped%20from%20visiting%20the%20Batadrava%20Than%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%2015th-century%20Vaishnavite%20religious%20leader%2C%20Srimanta%20Sankardev.%20Subsequently%2C%20Gandhi%C2%A0%20sat%C2%A0%20down%20on%20the%20road%20along%20with%20other%20Congress%20supporters%20who%20sang%20%E2%80%98Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20and%20above%20since%20(the)%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20helpless%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20people%20my%20district%20Porbandar%20and%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modhwadia%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20the%20BJP%20comes%20days%20before%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20enters%20the%20state%20on%20March%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20had%20been%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20over%20four%20decades%20and%20had%20served%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20along%20with%20being%20state%20unit%20chief.%20In%20the%202022%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20defeated%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Babu%20Bokhiria%20in%20Porbandar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Modhwadia%20had%20lent%20his%20support%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgujarat%2Fgujarat-assembly-passes-resolution-hailing-pm-for-ram-temple-event-congress-aap-support-it-2880579%5C%22%3Eunanimous%20resolution%20%3C%2Fa%3Epassed%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20lauding%20Modi%20for%20the%20successful%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20Speaking%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20Modhwadia%20said%20that%20it%20was%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20who%20had%20allowed%20the%20foundation%20stone%20laying%20ceremony%20at%20the%20site%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20however%2C%20Modhwadia%20had%20been%20a%20staunch%20critic%20of%20Modi%2C%20and%20had%20also%20drawn%20the%20ire%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20reprimanded%20Modhwadia%20for%20referring%20to%20Modi%20as%20a%20monkey%20who%20had%20challenged%20the%20lion%20(Manmohan%20Singh)%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgujarat-assembly-elections%2Fec-reprimands-modhwadia-for-his-remarks-against-narendra-modi%2Farticleshow%2F17595975.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%20in%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Modhwadia%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2056-inch%20chest%20and%20said%20only%20%E2%80%9Cdonkeys%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2056%20inches%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fit%20person%20has%20a%20chest%20of%2036%20inches%2C%20a%20body-builder%20can%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2042%2C%20it%20is%20only%20donkeys%20who%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2056%20inches%2C%20and%20bulls%20have%20a%20chest%20of%20100%20inches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2019%2FApr%2F09%2Fonly-donkeys-can-have-56-inch-chest-gujarat-congress-leader-arjun-modhwadia-1962332.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20had%20also%20questioned%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20air%20travels%20during%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20was%20Gujarat%20CM%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20travelled%20by%20air%2056%20times%20on%20government%20expense%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Now%2C%20BJP%20should%20repay%20that%20money%20to%20the%20government%20treasury%20and%20Modi%20should%20explain%20such%20serious%20allegations%20about%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modhwadia%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmodi-should-give-explanation-about-his-air-travels-arjun-modhwadia%2Farticleshow%2F39898026.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709647172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05175110%2FUntitled-design-30.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-gujarat-congress-chief-arjun-modhwadia-joins-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20staunch%20critic%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Modhwadia%20quit%20the%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20and%20said%20that%20the%20party%20had%20failed%20to%20assess%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20with%20its%20decision%20to%20decline%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-gujarat-congress-chief-arjun-modhwadia-joins-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Container%20Ship%20Attacked%20Near%20Red%20Sea%2C%20Navy%20Comes%20To%20The%20Rescue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMSC%20Sky%20II%2C%20a%20Liberia-flagged%20container%20ship%20with%20Indians%20onboard%2C%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Djibouti%20from%20Singapore%2C%20navigating%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20in%20the%20sea.%20Yesterday%2C%20around%20140%20km%20southeast%20of%20Aden%20in%20Yemen%2C%20the%20ship%20was%20attacked%20by%20Houthis.%20A%20distress%20call%20was%20made%20and%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20warships%20were%20in%20action%20for%20the%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINS%20Kolkata%2C%20a%20stealth%20Kolkata-class%20destroyer%2C%20is%20a%20frontline%20warship%20deployed%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20along%20with%20INS%20Kochi%20to%20safeguard%20the%20sea%20route%20from%20pirates%20and%20drone%20attacks.%20The%20container%20ship%20reported%20fire%20after%20a%20drone%2Fmissile%20attack%20from%20Houthi%20rebels%20from%20Yemen.%20INS%20Kolkata%20quickly%20responded%20to%20the%20distress%20and%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavy%20In%20Action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20specialised%20firefighting%20team%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20came%20on%20an%20inflatable%20motor%20boat%20and%20boarded%20the%20vessel.%20MSC%20Sky%20II%20had%2023%20crew%20members%2C%20including%2012%20Indians.%20A%20drone%2Fmissile%20reportedly%20fired%20by%20Houthis%20struck%20a%20container%20on%20the%20ship%20and%20the%20attack%20led%20to%20a%20massive%20fire.%20INS%20Kolkata%20was%20tailing%20the%20container%20ship%20while%20Navy%20personnel%20in%20firefighting%20gear%2C%20holding%20hose%20pipes%2C%20were%20in%20action%20to%20douse%20the%20flames.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianNavy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianNavy%3C%2Fa%3E%20swiftly%20responds%20to%20a%20Maritime%20Incident%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGulfofAden%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GulfofAden%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLiberian-flagged%20MV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMSCSkyII%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MSCSkyII%3C%2Fa%3E%20transiting%20approximately%2090%20Nm%20South%20East%20of%20Aden%20was%20reported%20on%20fire%20due%20to%20drone%2F%20missile%20attack%20PM%2004%20Mar.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINSKolkata%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23INSKolkata%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20mission%20deployed%20in%20the%20region%20for%20maritime%20security%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAG15Krocjr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAG15Krocjr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20SpokespersonNavy%20(%40indiannavy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findiannavy%2Fstatus%2F1764991296140198272%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Explosive%20Ordnance%20Disposal%20(EOD)%20team%20of%20the%20Navy%20were%20called%20for%20assistance%20with%20residual%20risk%20assessment.%20EOD%20is%20tasked%20with%20identifying%20and%20disposing%20of%20hazardous%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Navy%20helicopter%20provided%20cover%20and%20ensured%20reconnaissance%20during%20the%20operation.%20All%20crew%20members%20were%20safely%20escorted%20to%20safe%20waters%20and%20the%20operation%20was%20a%20success%2C%20with%20no%20injuries%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20Navy%20-%20Present%20Near%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20is%20among%20the%20latest%20strikes%20by%20the%20Iran-aligned%20Houthis%2C%20which%20have%20escalated%20since%20November%20last%20year.%20The%20Houthis%20have%20said%20they%20are%20targeting%20commercial%20ships%20in%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20is%20an%20important%20trade%20route%20that%20connects%20the%20Red%20Sea%20with%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Attacks%20from%20Houthis%2C%20coupled%20with%20piracy%20attempts%20have%20affected%20the%20sea%20trade%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20region%2C%20threatening%20global%20sea%20trade%20between%20the%20West%20and%20the%20East%2C%20which%20passes%20through%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20a%20toll%20gate%20in%20the%20maritime%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20a%20blue%20water%20navy%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20(IOR)%2C%20has%20deployed%20two%20warships%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%2010%20in%20the%20Northern%20and%20Western%20Arabian%20Sea.%20The%20deployment%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20US-led%20alliance%20in%20the%20region%20and%20the%20active%20presence%20to%20counter%20anti-hijacking%20and%20rescue%20missions%20is%20a%20dynamic%20shift.%20The%20Navy%20regularly%20patrols%20and%20responds%20to%20distress%20calls%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20MARCOS%20(Marine%20Commandos)%20have%20rescued%20crew%20from%20hijacked%20ships%20and%20assisted%20merchant%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BWill%20Teach%20A%20Hard%20Lesson%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Navy%20won't%20allow%20the%20security%20and%20safety%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20to%20be%20disrupted%20and%20will%20teach%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20hard%26quot%3B%20lesson%20if%20piracy%20is%20attempted%2C%20Navy%20chief%2C%20Admiral%20R%20Hari%20Kumar%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20our%20position%20very%20clear.%20It's%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20us.%20We%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20importance%20to%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20freedom%20of%20commerce%20in%20that%20region.%20Whatever%20is%20happening%20there%20not%20only%20us%20but%20also%20impacts%20the%20economic%20interests%20of%20so%20many%20people.%20%C2%A0We%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20our%20position%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20unfolding%20situation%20with%20close%20watch%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20our%20interests%20which%20have%20impacted%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20have%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20patrolling%20the%20area.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20secure%20the%20area%20and%20do%20their%20best%20so%20that%20our%20economic%20interests%20will%20not%20be%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20region%20in%20which%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20surface%20vessels%20are%20currently%20deployed%20to%20combat%20piracy%20has%20a%20surface%20area%20of%202.5%20million%20square%20nautical%20miles%2C%20making%20it%20very%20daunting%20to%20patrol%20for%20any%20single%20navy%2C%26quot%3B%20writes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fresearch%2Fdynamic-shift-indian-navy-in-the-red-sea%5C%22%3EHarsh%20V%20Pant%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Observers%20Research%20Foundation%20(ORF).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709647080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fie3nf5rg_ins-kolkata-_625x300_05_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-container-ship-attacked-near-red-sea-navy-comes-to-the-rescue-5181895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MSC%20Sky%20II%2C%20a%20Liberia-flagged%20container%20ship%20with%20Indians%20onboard%2C%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Djibouti%20from%20Singapore%2C%20navigating%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20in%20the%20sea.%20Yesterday%2C%20around%20140%20km%20southeast%20of%20Aden%20in%20Yemen%2C%20the%20ship%20was%20attacked%20by%20Houthis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-container-ship-attacked-near-red-sea-navy-comes-to-the-rescue-5181895%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-container-ship-attacked-near-re