elated%20fees%20at%20%C2%A31%2C570%20(approximately%20Rs%201.65%20lakh)%2C%20and%20Finland%2C%20which%20also%20has%20stringent%20requirements.%20It%20offers%20the%20EU%20Blue%20Card%2C%20but%20has%20a%20high%20earnings%20threshold%20of%20%E2%82%AC62%2C508%20(approximately%20Rs%2056%20lakh)%20for%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.william-russell.com%2Fblog%2Fhardest-countries-expats-relocate%2F%23hardest%5C%22%3EWilliam%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20expat%20insurance%20provider%20%E2%80%93%20analysed%2030%20countries%20and%20factors%20such%20as%20expat%20population%2C%20visa%20data%2C%20required%20vaccines%20and%20language%20requirements%20to%20determine%20the%20hardest%20countries%20to%20emigrate%20to.%20They%20gave%20each%20factor%20a%20normalised%20score%20out%20of%20ten%2C%20before%20taking%20an%20average%20of%20these%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20India%20has%20a%20low%20expat%20population%20percentage%20of%200.4%25%2C%20the%20visa%20demands%20significant%20fees%2C%20and%20at%20least%20three%20vaccinations%20are%20required%20to%20emigrate%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20the%20number%20of%20expats%20currently%20residing%20in%20a%20country%20gives%20us%20a%20general%20idea%20of%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20for%20people%20to%20move%20there%20and%20how%20appealing%20it%20is%20to%20expats.%20It%20also%20provides%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20easy%20it%20will%20be%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20new%20country%2C%20which%20is%20always%20easier%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20already%20a%20significant%20expat%20community.%20Remarkably%2C%20just%200.4%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20were%20born%20outside%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20top%20of%20routine%20vaccinations%20such%20as%20measles-mumps-rubella%20(MMR)%2C%20most%20travellers%20to%20India%20require%20vaccinations%20for%20hepatitis%20A%2C%20tetanus%20and%20typhoid.%20On%20top%20of%20these%2C%20some%20travellers%20may%20also%20need%20to%20be%20vaccinated%20against%20cholera%2C%20hepatitis%20B%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20rabies%20and%20tuberculosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20the%20lengthiest%20processing%20time%2C%20taking%20between%2010%20to%2011%20months%20(or%2041%20weeks)%2C%20whereas%20India%20processes%20applications%20in%20approximately%2010%20to%2015%20working%20days.%20Australia%20typically%20takes%20four%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20while%20Finland%E2%80%99s%20processing%20time%20is%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20countries%20that%20are%20easier%20to%20emigrate%20to%20are%20Hungary%2C%20Malta%20and%20Austria.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709643824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05143745%2Fimage-1906.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-tops-list-as-most-challenging-country-for-expats-to-relocate-to-finds-study%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20a%20low%20expat%20population%20percentage%20of%200.4%25%2C%20the%20visa%20demands%20significant%20fees%2C%20and%20at%20least%20three%20vaccinations%20are%20required%20to%20emigrate%20to%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-tops-list-as-most-challenging-country-for-expats-to-relocate-to-finds-study%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Worse%20than%209%2F11'%3A%20Musk%20attacks%20Biden%20over%20'illegal%20immigrants'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709642919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108241111%2Cimgsize-555289.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fworse-than-9%2F11-musk-attacks-biden-over-illegal-immigrants%2Farticleshow%2F108241115.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3