s%20of%20election%20funding.%20This%20was%20done%20by%20way%20of%20arrests%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fhigher-cash-seizures-being-recorded-by-i-t-dept-every-assembly-polls-cbdt-2879089%5C%22%3Esearch%20and%20seizure%20of%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20campaigns%20for%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2Fno-claimants-for-699-crore-cash-and-valuables-seized-says-chief-electoral-officer%2Farticle67566608.ece%5C%22%3Eno%20claimants%20for%20Rs%20700%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20seized%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20the%20target%20of%20the%20enforcement%20agencies%20is%20the%20opposition.%20They%20won%E2%80%99t%20dare%20touch%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Has%20Become%20an%20Excessive%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgencies%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98laundry%20list%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20have%20a%20devious%20track%20record.%20During%20the%20Modi%20years%2C%20they%20became%20the%20chief%20instrument%20of%20repression.%20Political%20opponents%20were%20targeted%20on%20unsubstantiated%20grounds.%20Their%20raids%20have%20become%20an%20everyday%20occurrence.%20Hardly%20a%20day%20passes%20without%20the%20ED%20raiding%20or%20serving%20notices%20on%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-rules-political-leaders-not-immune-to-law-as-opposition-parties-demand-fresh-guidelines-for-arrest-remand-and-bail-politicalleaders-legalimmunity-supremecourt-oppositionparties-cbi-ed-arrest-remand-bail-guidelines-