JP%20leaders%20are%20never%20raided%20or%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20sound%20sleep%20as%20there%20are%20no%20inquiries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maharashtra%20politician%20Harshvardhan%20Patil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-wont-come-after-me-since-i-am-a-bjp-mp-sanjay-patil%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20colleague%20Sanjay%20Patil%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20after%20me%20since%20I%20am%20a%20BJP%20MP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20many%20such%20boasts%20by%20the%20relieved%20victims%20of%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fshashi-tharoor-shares-list-politicians-graft-probe-bjp-8470853%2F%5C%22%3EShashi%20Tharoor%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98laundered%E2%80%99%20defectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20such%20big%20men%20as%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(now%20the%20high-profile%20Assam%20CM)%2C%20Bhawana%20Gawli%2C%20Yashwant%20Jadhav%2C%20Yamini%20Jadhav%20and%20Pratap%20Sarnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdded%20to%20this%20was%20another%20list%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2F7-politicians-with-corruption-charges-cbi-and-ed-wont-raid%2F280173%2F%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20Ramesh%20Pokhriyal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20others%20like%20Mukul%20Roy%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20who%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20first%20targeted%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20%E2%80%98forget%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20cases%20against%20him%20when%20he%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20finally%20relaunched%20the%20cases%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20and%20CBI%20under%20Modi%20have%20been%20resorting%20to%20such%20cloak%20and%20dagger%20operations%20that%20has%20been%20part%20of%20those%20conducted%20by%20all%20hardened%20dictators%