0MLAs%2C%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20were%20told%20that%20the%20ED%20will%20arrest%20him%20soon%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20will%20be%20toppled.%20For%20his%20revealing%20this%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fthey-are-only-here-to-do-nautanki-aap-defends-arvind-kejriwal-against-notice-on-mlas-poaching-issue-416071-2024-02-03%5C%22%3Ethe%20Delhi%20police%20went%20to%20his%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20serve%20a%20notice%20to%20him%20demanding%20evidence%20for%20his%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20reportedly%20insisted%20that%20they%20hand%20over%20the%20notice%20in%20person%20to%20Kejriwal%2C%20AAP%20leaders%20present%20there%20sought%20to%20know%20under%20which%20law%20they%20were%20required%20to%20serve%20the%20notice%20directly%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20time%20ago%2C%20Shah%20had%20alleged%20that%20Meghalaya%20leader%20Conrad%20Sangma%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20corrupt%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister.%20This%20was%20before%20Sangma%20became%20a%20BJP%20ally.%20AAP%20leaders%20ask%20why%20the%20CBI%20or%20the%20police%20%E2%80%93%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20serve%20notice%20to%20Shah.%20They%20ask%3A%20Why%20such%20double%20standards%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMisuse%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20has%20been%20so%20widespread%20that%20former%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.madhyamam.com%2Findia%2Fashok-gehlot-criticises-ed-says-they-roam-around-more-than-stray-dogs-1219029%5C%22%3EAshok%20Gehlot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yugmarg.com%2Fnews%2F19001-more-than-dogs-and-cats-personnel-of-ed-it-moving-around-chhattisgarh-cm-baghel%5C%22%3EBhupesh%20Baghel%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20said%20there%20were%20more%20ED%20officials%20on%20the%20prowl%20than%20stray%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20ED%20officials%20have%20been%20caught%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegra