ering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20case%20against%20Shivakumar%20in%202018%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdk-shivakumar-arrested-ed-money-laundering%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20on%20September%203%2C%202019.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20granted%20him%20bail%20on%20October%2023%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202017%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20had%20alleged%20that%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%208.59%20crore%20was%20seized%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20deputy%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Safdarjung%20Enclave%20apartment%20in%20Delhi%2C%20based%20on%20which%20a%20case%20was%20framed%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20he%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20premises%20linked%20to%20Shivakumar%20at%20a%20time%20when%20he%20sheltered%2044%20MLAs%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20from%20Gujarat%20at%20a%20resort%20outside%20Bengaluru%20ahead%20of%20a%20crucial%20Rajya%20Sabha%20poll%20in%20the%20western%20state.%20Late%20Congress%20leader%20Ahmed%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20were%20dependent%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fahmed-patel-to-shivakumar-i-owe-rs-victory-to-your-efforts%2Farticleshow%2F59996638.cms%5C%22%3E44%20MLAs%20hosted%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20multiple%20properties%20of%20Shivakumar%20were%20searched%20on%20various%20occasions%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20his%20daughter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fed-summons-dk-shivakumars-daughter%2Farticle61987298.ece%5C%22%3EAishwarya%20Shivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fed-summons-dks-wife-mother%2Farticle29684269.ece%5C%22%3Emother%20D.K.%20Gowramma%20and%20wife%20Usha%20Shivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20also%20issued%20summons%20by%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnational-herald-ed-again-summons-karnataka-congress-chief-d-k-shivakumar%5C%22%3Esummoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20ED%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20separate%20money%20laundering%20probe%20into%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20Congress%20party-owned%20National%20Herald%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20SC%20dismisses%20the%20longstanding%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20allowed%20the%20special%20leave%20petitions%20filed%20by%20Shivakumar%20and%20his%20aide%20Anjaneya%20Hanumanthaiah%20against%20a%202019%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20verdict%20upholding%20the%20summonses%20issued%20to%20them%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20as%20per%20the%3Cem%3E%20Live%20Law%20r%3C%2Fem%3Eeport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Shivakumar%20had%20approached%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20and%20sought%20dismissal%20of%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20ED.%20However%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20Shivakumar%20and%20others%20in%20August%202019%2C%20upholding%20the%20central%20agency%E2%80%99s%20summonses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20reason%20cited%20by%20the%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20was%20that%20section%20120B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20constituted%20a%20stand-alone%20offence%20adequate%20to%20invoke%20the%20PMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20congress%20president%20and%20his%20aide%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20apex%20court%20held%20the%20high%20court%20bench%E2%80%99s%20rationale%20as%20%E2%80%98unsustainable%E2%80%99%20in%20view%20of%20its%20recent%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3EThe%20Great%20Crossover%3A%20Opposition%20Leaders%20Who%20Joined%20the%20BJP%20After%20Action%20by%20Central%20Agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20case%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20ruled%20that%20Section%20120B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20becomes%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20%E2%80%9Conly%20when%20the%20conspiracy%20is%20directed%20towards%20committing%20an%20offence%20that%20is%20otherwise%20scheduled.%20The%20legislative%20intent%20behind%20the%20PMLA%20was%20not%20to%20make%20every%20offence%20not%20included%20in%20the%20schedule%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20by%20applying%20Section%20120B%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SC%20bend%20had%20noted%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20a%20review%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20against%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Shivkumar%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20underlined%20that%20if%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20review%20petition%20related%20to%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment%20is%20accepted%2C%20then%20the%20direction%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20in%20the%20impugned%20judgment%20would%20stand%20affirmed%2C%20allowing%20the%20ED%20to%20seek%20a%20review%20or%20recall%20of%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20latest%20order%20if%20necessary%2C%20as%20per%20the%3Cem%3E%20Live%20La%3C%2Fem%3Ew%20report.%C2%A0%3Cb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709640858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05163809%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-05-at-4.37.39-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-cm-dk-shivakumar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20En