0the%20former%20Yugoslavia%20for%20example%2C%20states%20that%20everyone%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20decide%E2%80%9D%20whether%20to%20bear%20children%20%E2%80%93%20France%20is%20the%20only%20country%20to%20take%20it%20further%20and%20explicitly%20guarantee%20that%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20change%20is%20being%20made%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrance-macron-promises-to-make-abortion-rights-irreversible%2Fa-67249137%5C%22%3Epromised%20the%20measure%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%202022%20rolling%20back%20of%20abortion%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Elysee%20Palace%20has%20proposed%20that%20Article%2034%20of%20the%20French%20constitution%20be%C2%A0amended%20to%20specify%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20law%20determines%20the%20conditions%20by%20which%20is%20exercised%20the%20freedom%20of%20women%20to%20have%20recourse%20to%20an%20abortion%2C%20which%20is%20guaranteed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%E2%80%99s%20government%20aims%C2%A0to%20make%20%E2%80%9Ca%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20have%20an%20abortion%20irreversible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20vote%2C%20Macron%20said%20France%20was%20sending%20a%20%E2%80%9Cuniversal%20message%E2%80%9D%20by%20defending%20abortion%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20happening%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Assembly%2C%20France%E2%80%99s%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%2C%20overwhelmingly%20approved%20making%20abortion%20a%20%E2%80%9Cguaranteed%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20constitution.%20The%20country%E2%80%99s%20upper%20house%2C%20the%20Senate%2C%20did%20the%20same%20last%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20congress%20of%20both%20houses%20met%20at%C2%A0Versailles%2C%20where%20the%20lawmakers%20eventually%20gave%20it%20the%20three-fifths%20supermajority%20needed%20for%20a%20constitutional%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20want%20to%20attack%20the%20freedoms%20of%20a%20people%2C%20we%20always%20start%20with%20that%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20French%20Prime%20Minister%20Gabriel%20Attal%20told%20those%20gathered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20freedoms%20are%20inherently%20threatened.%20Inherently%20fragile%2C%20in%20essence%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20those%20who%20decide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20had%20faced%20initial%20resistance%20in%20the%20right-leaning%20Senate.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20represented%20in%20parliament%20has%20questioned%20the%20right%20to%20abortion%2C%20which%20France%20decriminalised%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVatican%2C%20French%20bishops%20oppose%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fabortion-us-marks-a-year-since-roe-v-wade-reversal%2Fa-66013358%5C%22%3Ereverse%20the%20%3Cem%3ERoe%20v.%20Wade%3C%2Fem%3E%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recognised%20women%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20right%20to%20abortion%2C%20prompted%20activists%20to%20press%20for%20France%20to%20make%20the%20constitutional%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20this%20event%20is%20not%20isolated%3A%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20even%20in%20Europe%2C%20there%20are%20currents%20of%20opinion%20that%20seek%20to%20hinder%20at%20any%20cost%20the%20freedom%20of%20women%20to%20terminate%20their%20pregnancy%20if%20they%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20introduction%20to%20the%20bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vatican%20on%20Monday%20repeated%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20change%2C%20echoing%20concerns%20already%20raised%20by%20French%20Catholic%20bishops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Pontifical%20Academy%20for%20Life%20recalls%20that%20in%20the%20era%20of%20universal%20human%20rights%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20%E2%80%98right%E2%80%99%20to%20take%20a%20human%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Vatican%20institution%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrance-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right%2Fa-68434557%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709637905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05165119%2Fimage-1907.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffrance-becomes-the-first-country-to-make-abortion-a-constitutional-right%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20lawmakers%20have%20approved%20a%20historic%20Bill%20that%20would%20enshrine%20a%20woman's%20right%20to%20an%20abortion%20in%20the%20constitution.%20No%20other%20country%20in%20the%20world%20has%20granted%20that%20level%20of%20protection%20to%20the%20right%20to%20end%20pregnancy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffrance-becomes-the-first-country-to-make-abortion-a-constitutional-right%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Hamas%20war%3A%20Only%20two-state%20solution%20will%20deliver%20enduring%20peace%2C%20India%20says%20at%20UNGA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709637781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108238184%2Cimgsize-1222418.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fisrael-hamas-war-only-two-state-solution-will-deliver-enduring-peace-india-says-at-unga%2Farticleshow%2F108219564.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108219564.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%20condemns%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20at%20the%20UN%2C%20urging%20for%20a%20t