0a%20major%20expose%20in%202019%2C%20revealing%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20flaws%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20accountability%20in%20political%20funding%2C%20which%20finally%20resulted%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20banning%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20declared%20in%202019%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20had%20iterated%20its%202013%20advisory%20against%20the%20use%20of%20photos%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdefence%20personnel%20by%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Celection%20propaganda%E2%80%9D%20after%20former%20naval%20chief%20Admiral%20L.%20Ramdas%20complained%20about%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20posters%20that%20featured%20an%20image%20of%20Wing%20Commander%20V.%20Abhinandan%2C%20who%20was%20released%20by%20Pakistan%20after%20his%20fighter%20jet%20was%20shot%20down%20over%20its%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20commission%20that%20some%20political%20parties%20are%20using%20the%20photographs%20of%20the%20Defence%20personnel%20in%20advertisement%20as%20part%20of%20their%20political%20campaigns%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20noted%20in%20its%20March%209%2C%202019%20advisory.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20a%20nation%20are%20the%20guardian%20of%20its%20frontiers%2C%20security%20and%20the%20political%20system.%20They%20are%20apolitical%20and%20neutral%20stakeholders%20in%20a%20modern%20democracy.%20It%20is%20therefore%20necessary%20that%20the%20political%20parties%20and%20leaders%20exercise%20great%20caution%20while%20making%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20their%20political%20campaigns%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20added.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20March%2019%2C%202019%20the%20ECI%20had%20issued%20another%20advisory%20extending%20to%20social%20media%20against%20any%20electioneering%20about%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20underlined%20the%20repeated%20instances%20of%20violation%20of%20the%20advisory%20by%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%20for%20using%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Ci%3Eji%20ki%20sena%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Ghaziabad%20on%20March%2031%2C%202019%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20cross-border%20strikes%20by%20Indian%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%209%2C%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20in%20Latur%3A%20%E2%80%9CMy%20first-time%20voters%2C%20can%20you%20dedicate%20your%20first%20vote%20to%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20air%20strike%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balakot%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20on%20April%2025%2C%202019%20the%20prime%20minister%20repeated%20the%20Balakot%20pitch%20in%20Varanasi.%20On%20April%2021%2C%20Modi%20said%20in%20Barmer%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20we%20kept%20it%20(the%20nuclear%20button)%20for%20Diwali%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20same%20day%2C%20he%20said%20in%20Patan%3A%20%E2%80%9CPakistan%20announced%20the%20return%20of%20the%20pilot%E2%80%A6%20else%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ci%3Eqatal%20ki%20raat%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20Batra%20had%20also%20complained%20against%20a%20BJP%20hoarding%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20image%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%E2%80%9CEntered%20the%20home%20of%20the%20enemy%20and%20attacked%20the%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F