operations%20with%20all%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20violating%20ground%20rules%20and%20attacking%20Meiteis%20during%20the%20ethnic%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Names%20of%20Places%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20on%20March%204%2C%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20criminalised%20attempts%20made%20by%20any%20person%20to%20refer%20to%20some%20places%20with%20their%20own%20names%20in%20official%20statements%2C%20etc.%20From%20the%20instances%20given%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20at%20the%20House%2C%20it%20comes%20across%20that%20the%20law%20was%20particularly%20aimed%20at%20stalling%20the%20Kuki%20community%20to%20act%20otherwise.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20Lamka%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20made%20a%20specific%20reference%20to%20this%20particular%20example%20in%20the%20House%20on%20March%204%2C%20stating%20that%20Churachandpur%20was%20named%20after%20Maharaja%20Churachand%20(of%20Manipur%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community)%20in%20honour%20of%20his%20contributions%20made%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20territorial%20boundary%20of%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20no%20one%20is%20authorised%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20a%20place%20or%20site%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20authority%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fhouse-passes-manipur-names-of-places-bill-2024%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20Imphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20mentioned%20use%20of%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Lamka%20district%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20Churachandpur%20district%20in%20an%20official%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ongoing%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20several%20instances%20came%20to%20light%20where%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20change%20names%20on%20community%20lines%2C%20including%20a%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fin-suspected-hacking-imphal-airport-ticketing-office-called-lamka-on-e-tickets%5C%22%3Esuspected%20hacking%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Air%20India%E2%80%99s%20ticketing%20office%20(ATO)%20at%20Imphal%20in%20July%20last%20year.%20Tickets%20issued%20to%20passengers%20at%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20were%20printed%20as%20ATO%2C%20Lamka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20complaints%20made%20by%20the%20Meitei%20passengers%2C%20MLA%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20R.%20Imo%20Singh%2C%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20civil%20aviation%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20to%20rectify%20the%20mistake%20and%20initiate%20an%20investigation%20into%20it%20immediately.%20Note%20that%20as%20of%20now%2C%20Kukis%20cannot%20access%20the%20Imphal%20airport%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20facility%20in%20the%20state%20providing%20connectivity%20outside%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20historical%20hill%20%E2%80%98Thangjing%E2%80%99%20was%20found%20trying%20to%20change%20into%20%E2%80%98Thangting%E2%80%99%20and%20Thangjing%20hill%20as%20Mount%20Olive%20and%20a%20reserved%20forest%20as%20%E2%80%98Haokip%20Reserve%20Forest%E2%80%99.%20Even%20some%20groups%20produced%20documents%20regarding%20the%20%E2%80%98Haokip%20Reserve%20Forest%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20unexpected%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20House%20on%20March%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20any%20attempt%20by%20an%20officer%20found%20involved%20in%20the%20alteration%20of%20any%20name%20from%20the%20official%20ones%20would%20be%20prosecuted%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20be%20imprisoned%20up%20to%20three%20years%20and%20Rs%201-3%20lakh%20(fine)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709632142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%